ang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\ncolor:green\"><o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:list 18.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:green\">1）</span></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:green\">白色药片不变色或略有浅蓝色均为阳性结果，不变蓝为强阳性结果，说明农药残留量较高。</span></u></b><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\ncolor:green\"><o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:list 18.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:green\">2）</span></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:green\">显浅蓝色为弱阳性结果，说明农药残留量相对较低。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:green\"><o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;\r\ntab-stops:list 18.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:green\">3）</span></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:green\">白色药片变为天蓝色或与空白对照卡相同，为阴性结果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:green\"><o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">结论：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\ncolor:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:red;background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">以上这一批次的<span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span>农药有机肥蔬菜依然合格！</span></u></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\nbackground:silver;mso-highlight:silver\">注：以上的反应只对含有有机磷和氨基甲酸酯的剧毒农药反应，基本上覆盖所有品种的剧毒农药，但不包含低毒农药，目前也没有任何简单几种实验能覆盖所有的农药品种，所以只能检测出剧毒类。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1358372128', '', '0', 'http://', '每月农残速测监督展示');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('179', '6', '蔬菜套餐操作界面解说', '<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">原味生活独自开发的套餐管理界面，比较人性化和方便，具体操作介绍如下：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#FF6600\">步骤一：首先登陆自己的账号，然后进入<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>我的原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，接着看左侧的命令条，找到最下面的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>套餐管理<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，选择你购买的套餐。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/1(4).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">步骤二：选择你需要确定配送的日期，右侧则会自动弹出需要选择的蔬菜品种。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/2(5).jpg\" width=\"801\" height=\"597\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">步骤三：除了固定品种外，选择好剩余品种，及填入相应的数量，并选择好配送到的取菜点。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/3(2).jpg\" width=\"810\" height=\"585\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">步骤四：选择好后，务必别忘了，点击更新套餐配置！</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/4(4).jpg\" width=\"795\" height=\"519\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">步骤五：弹出更新成功才算行了。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/5(3).jpg\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/5(3).jpg\" width=\"798\" height=\"501\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">步骤六：选择确定后，再回头看看，则发现确定选择的蔬菜已经显示灰色。以后只要是在系统自动遮断之前，均可以自由调整。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/2121(1).jpg\" width=\"825\" height=\"498\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red\">注意点：以下的内容请详细读一读，违规的操作，则无法提交套餐。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">原味生活首创&mdash;&mdash;满足会员喜好的订餐系统说明：</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#666666\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">①、我们为您列出了当前有效的套餐。如果发现您的套餐没有显示可能是您没有支付的原因。如果是其他原因请联系客服人员。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#666666\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">②、请点击某个日期配置该天为您配送的商品，默认<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>个农场固定的商品（尽量会以大家喜爱的品种为主，重量为<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>斤），其他的为自由选择。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#666666\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">③、点击想选择的蔬菜，边框则会显示红色；具体的数量，如<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>，则表示<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>斤；如是您购买的<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>人套餐，则 在该天一共有<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>个自由选择的蔬菜品种，若是您购买的<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>人套餐，则剩下<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>个自由选择的蔬菜品种，以此类推。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#666666\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">④、自由选择蔬菜的系统最小订餐单位为<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>斤，若是有特殊要求的会员，请您单独联系客服人员。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#666666\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">⑤、正确的选择好您要的蔬菜品种及数量后，请务必记得选择离您最近的取菜点，并进行更新套餐配置，否则不会记录到数据库里。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#666666\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">⑥、请您务必在每次的配送日的前日<span lang=\"EN-US\">am:10</span>点前将您的订餐计划确定完毕，超过这个时间后，系统将自动关闭套餐更新配置，您的更改将不再生效。因为蔬菜的上市会比较随机，不建议一次性配置完毕。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#666666\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">⑦、其他不懂事宜尽请咨询客服人员，谢谢！</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#666666\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/6(2).jpg\" width=\"789\" height=\"561\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/5(2).jpg\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/2(4).jpg\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1358379543', '', '0', 'http://', '0农药有机肥套餐操作界面解说');
