rmal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">左边的有机芋头的叶脉清晰整齐。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有机农产品的国外调查：<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span></span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日本北海道有机农业协同组合曾于<span lang=\"EN-US\">92</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">93</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">94</span>年，从<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>个方面调查人们对有机食品的感受（评分规则：<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>分最高、良好<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>分、一般<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>分、略差<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>分、差劲<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>分），最终结果如下：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 120%;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 120%; font-family: 宋体;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/21.jpg\" width=\"256\" height=\"175\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"line-height: 120%; font-family: 宋体;\">（注）<span lang=\"EN-US\">N</span>为体验过有机食品的调查人数 </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 120%; font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可以说有机食品除了安全外，绝大多数人认为有机农产品是很好吃的。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1360040536', '', '0', 'http://', '')