ages/upload/Image/ss30(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">近来风很大，农场将大棚改小了，因为风大，薄膜还没覆盖上去。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss31(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">10个品种的西红柿，都下地了，哈哈哈~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss33(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss34(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">茄子移栽后还没完全缓过来。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss35(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">薄皮辣椒是缓过来了~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss36(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss37(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">风太大，薄膜都掀开了，堆肥发酵温度不够高。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss38.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></strong></span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1364938391', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('271', '18', '探访孟河镇罗妃鲜酱油的制作过程', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 郑纪苟老先生是孟河镇万绥人，近日，他带着收集的照片和资料找到了晚报：&ldquo;过去做的土酱油你们感兴趣吗？我们万绥人年年都做罗妃鲜酱油，灵得很啊！&rdquo;我们曾在去年十月初一那天，正巧在万绥拍到过当地人下酱油的场景，再加上此次郑老先生拿来的资料，刚好可以合上一幅完整的罗妃鲜酱油制作过程图。在如今的万绥，很多人家还保留着年年此时做酱油的传统。采访中，听到最多的就是村民们说这种酱油如何如何鲜美。乖乖！酱油是没吃到，可眉毛还是差点被说他们说鲜掉一半。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 每年农历十月初一，是孟河镇万绥人下酱油的那一天。下酱油就是把事先烧熟、晾干、发酶后的黄豆放入盛满盐水的酱缸中继续发酵，最后制成酱油的过程。这里的酱油，就是鼎鼎有名的罗妃鲜酱油，罗妃，乃南北朝时南朝梁武帝的爱妃&ldquo;罗妃娘娘&rdquo;，而下酱油的这一天，正是此罗妃娘娘的忌日，老百姓为了纪念这位娘娘，特选此吉日，而传说中，罗妃娘娘也会保佑在这天下的酱油成为上乘之品。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>热心的郑老先生，想让老母亲自制酱豆，成功了一大半</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 万绥人郑纪苟老先生退休后的乐趣就是收集、整理有关齐梁文化的事物，几年前，罗妃鲜酱油也引起了他的注意，原来，自己从小吃的自制酱油竟是创说中由罗妃娘娘流传下来的！郑先生来了兴致，一面四处打听、收集着有关罗妃和酱油的故事，一面在附近几个村庄走动，看看还有多少人家如今还在做着这种酱油。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 秋天的时候，郑老先生将自己80多岁的老母亲请出了山，想让老太太再做一次罗妃鲜酱油。老太太上一次做这种酱油，已经是很多年前的事了，难免有些手生，可架不住儿子的热情，还是捋起袖子做起来，郑老先生也没闲着，将老母亲制作的过程用相机详细地记录了下来。做酱油，第一步就是自制酱豆，以下图片，记录的就是从黄豆到酱豆的酶变过程。唯一可惜的是，做到最后一步，老太太的&ldquo;路基&rdquo;叶（万绥当地的叫法，就是高粱叶子，&ldquo;路&rdquo;和罗妃的&ldquo;罗&rdquo;同音）、稻草放得太多了，太巴结了，结果，黄豆酶变过了头。以下就是郑老先生记录下的自制酱豆的过程。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ww1(3).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 图1：深秋季节，选优质的黄豆5-10斤，在水中浸泡、洗净。再将它们放入锅中，煮沸，称之为&ldquo;煮酱豆&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ww2(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 图2：煮烂后的毛豆，要浸在锅中一整夜，让它们变得&ldquo;熟烂粗胖&rdquo;。第二天一早捞出来，放在院子里晾干。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ww3(2).jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 图3：豆子晾干后，均匀地拌上元麦粉，这一步叫做&ldquo;拌酱豆&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ww4(2).jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 图4：拌和好的豆，仍旧放在盘篮中，再在上面用&ldquo;路基&rdquo;叶子盖上一层。再在&ldquo;路基&rdquo;上头加盖一层稻草。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ww5(2).jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 图5：稻草上还要加一件衣服，也是进一步给酱豆保温。盘蓝底下要放一张&ldquo;芦菲&rdquo;（万绥当地的叫法，就是芦苇，&ldquo;芦&rdquo;和罗妃的&ldquo;罗&rdquo;同音），让豆子透气。大概7天左右，豆子就会发酵酶变，酶色以黄绿为佳，白色为差。最后，将酶变好的酱豆及时放在太阳下晾晒，等到农历&ldquo;十月早&rdquo;（十月初一），就可以下酱豆，做酱油了。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">阿珍家年年都做，十月初一正好赶上她下酱豆</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 郑老先生家的酱豆虽然没做成功，但他的邻居们，做成功的还是有的。去年十月初一那天，我们刚巧在万绥采访，遇到了村上阿珍家下酱豆。阿珍家年年都做酱油，原先是她的婆婆做，现在轮到她，总之一年都没断过。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 下酱豆的过程相对简单，把酱豆放入牛头缸（缸的形状和大小和牛头差不多）中，加满水，再加入盐、生姜以及少许辣椒（分量很少，最后制成的酱油中尝不到辣味）。然后在缸上盖上一层布，放入院子里即可，大概一个多月后，新鲜的酱油就制成了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 阿珍说，这样制成的酱油，别看他颜色淡淡的没卖相，实则相当鲜，用它做菜味精都不用放。这么一小缸酱油，全家人能吃到第二年的五六月份。7月后的整个下半年，就该吃那些从酱油中捞出的酱豆了，做味道淡的蔬菜时少许放一点，立即能让蔬菜可口不少哪。&ldquo;村子附近那些个厂子里的大老板们，什么没吃过？但就最喜欢吃我们这的酱油、酱豆，还向我们要哪！&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ww6(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 图6：把酱豆放入牛头缸中，加满水，再加入盐、生姜以及少许辣椒。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ww7(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 图7：用勺子加以搅拌，最后再缸上加上一层布即可。</span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1364943881', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('272', '18', '土榨菜籽油过程', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 家里吃的最多的是当地的山茶油，从小就吃惯这一口，像市场上的葵花籽、大豆、玉米花生之类的色拉油都不爱吃，除了山茶油之外，近年来越来越爱上菜油了，原本只在做煎炸面食的时候才用上菜油，如今烧段鱼，炒味可口的下饭菜也用菜油代替了，这样一来，母亲带来的10斤菜油很快就吃尽，打听到单位保洁阿姨家收割的油菜有自榨的菜油，便又买了10斤，10元一斤的价格也算是公道的。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 记得以往春末夏初时节，到农村去采访，往往人未进村便闻油香，那是土作坊里给村民代榨菜油。走进榨油坊，里面雾气腾腾，幽香四溢，油坊主忙而不乱，村民则挑着洋铁桶、塑料桶、陶罐等各种盛油器候着。待采访结束，又折回油坊，花上不到十元钱，买上一大可乐瓶的鲜榨茶油回家，真是一举两得的美事。若是遇到朴实的村民，一张十元纸币还你推我往的，末了很难为情地收下，然后把满满一壶菜油提到你手中，沉甸甸的菜油中更是浸沁着村民的善良和淳朴。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 下组照片应该是五六年前到芳村镇一个村采访，遇过一个榨油坊，粗粗见识了榨菜籽油的过程&mdash;&mdash;</span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd1(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">      芝麻粒一样的油菜籽放在大铁锅里翻炒，这是个体力活。</span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd2(3).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">      炒好的油菜籽还要放在灶上蒸。</span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd3(2).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">       在一个圆形的铁器里放上稻草，把蒸好的菜籽倒在上面，应该是进入做茶饼的程序了。 </span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd4(5).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">       原来这个环节要靠双脚来完成的，这个油坊主踢踏着一双脏兮兮的拖鞋呢。</span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd5(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">   别看我脚脏，我工作认真着呢。  </span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd6(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">       把 一组组茶饼叠加在机器上，就开始榨油了。山茶油的制作工艺和这个很相似，也有茶饼，现在很多山茶油企业就把农村里榨过油的茶饼买来，添加点其它杂油就成了品牌山茶油了，所以买油还是到这种榨油坊买才是货真价实，比起那些地沟油，咱坊主这双脏脚算得了什么。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1364944297', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('273', '18', '进口橄榄油加工过程和加工工艺流程', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana;\">榨取橄榄油的第一步是橄榄果的采摘：一般是在气候比较冷的季节进行，在西班牙，橄榄果的采摘通常是在11月份到1月份。首先必须说明的是树龄超过5年以上的油橄榄才开始产果，树龄20年左右的橄榄树是产果高峰期的开始，到树龄100年后产量才会开始下降，但是橄榄果的质量保持不变。</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">种植地中海得天独厚的气候条件孕育了橄榄树，温暖漫长的冬季，炎热干燥的夏季，充足的日照的沙地，非常适宜橄榄树的成长。</font></span><font face=\"Verdana\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">进口橄榄油</span></font><font face=\"Verdana\">在这种环境下也能产出高品质的橄榄油品牌．</font></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">采摘</font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">为获取高质量的油液，最重要的是保证橄榄果实绝对新鲜和完好。橄榄果的采摘按照自古以来的传统技术，几乎都是用手工来完成。这个过程中，最关键的是不能让果实受到撞击或切割之类的伤害，否则会引起发酵，影响橄榄油的质量。因此，收集橄榄油需要大量的劳动力，这也正是橄榄油的价格高于其他植物油的主要原因之一。  </font></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qw1.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">每天，大量刚采摘的橄榄被运到加工厂,第一次压榨产生的橄榄油品质较高，第二次和第三次压榨出的油品质稍低．</font></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">榨取</font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">为保证质量，橄榄果必须在采摘后的24小时内进行加工。如搁置时间过长，就有可能引起发酵，影响到油的香气和滋味。无论采用传统方式或现代方式，均完全采用物理手段对橄榄果进行加工，且温度始终保持在30℃以下。因此，进口橄榄油是现有使用油脂中唯一始终保持原始状态的油脂。  橄榄油其实不是橄榄果核压榨出来的油，而是真正的橄榄&ldquo;果汁&rdquo;，它来自橄榄果肉，这在所有种类的植物油中是独一无二的。其制取方法更是独特，只用纯物理方法冷压榨，因而是纯天然产品，而其他植物油一般均是从植物种子中采用化学溶剂或者加热提炼而来。  </font></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qw2.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"518\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"> </font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"> </font></span></p>\r\n<p><font face=\"Verdana\"><font face=\"Verdana\">这道工序在16到28摄氏度的环境下进行，以便让橄榄油拥有较高的品质,品质最高的橄榄油酸度低于0.8%。酸度越低，橄榄油品质越高。大多</font>橄榄油品牌的特级初榨橄榄油酸度都会小于0.8％．</font></p>\r\n<p><font face=\"Verdana\"> </font><font face=\"Verdana\">\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qw3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><font face=\"Verdana\">进口橄榄油加工过程和加工工艺流程</font><br />\r\n</strong><font face=\"Verdana\">有时候，大蒜、胡椒粉和其他配料会被添加入橄榄油以提高香味。<br />\r\n最终产品，玻璃瓶装橄榄油。高品质的橄榄油必须存放在黑色玻璃瓶中，以防止发生化学变化。</font></span></p>\r\n</font></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1364945766', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('274', '18', '全球最贵火腿制作过程 猪越黑越好放三年才能吃', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa1(2).jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"438\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">中国的金华火腿比较有名，不知道大家吃过没有。这个价格应该是老百姓都能接受的，但世上有一种火腿的价格可能不是我们普通人能够承受得起的，今期为大家介绍的就是西班牙顶级伊比利(Iberico)火腿，每条重七公斤，售价一千八百英镑(约合2万元人民币，每公斤折合人民币近2900元，这头猪也太值钱了。西班牙火腿世界闻名，可谓西班牙饮食文化&ldquo;国粹&rdquo;。就让我们走进西班牙去一探究竟，这种天价火腿到底是如何制成的。<!--page--></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa2(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 全球最贵的伊比利(Iberico)火腿17日开始在英国发售，每条重七公斤，售价一千八百英镑(约合2万元人民币，每公斤折合人民币近2900元)。这批火腿在伦敦牛津街塞尔弗里奇(Selfridges)百货公司发售，每条都有基因证书证明真伪。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa3(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 这批火腿的生产过程绝不简单，火腿专家马尔多纳多和猪农要精心挑选五十头猪，然后让它们在西班牙牧场生活，并要用特别饲料喂养，令火腿味道与别不同。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa4(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 屠夫把五十头猪宰杀后，切下猪腿，用盐腌长达三年，才放入手制的木盒发售。  塞尔弗里奇百货公司发言人说，这批火腿入口即融，非常美味，虽然价钱昂贵，但是与制作火腿所花的心机和时间比较，实在物超所值。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa5(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 西班牙火腿的制作并不复杂，主要是靠腌制而成，但切火腿确实需要一定的功夫。西班牙有专门切火腿的火腿师，不仅需要一定的天赋，而且还得经过四五年的专业训练。<!--page--></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa6.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 在西班牙，火腿师的技艺绝不亚于做大菜的厨师。最近，《环球时报》记者专门采访了一位火腿师胡安&middot;桑切斯。胡安已经有16年的切火腿经验，他的家乡在安达卢西亚，这里是西班牙火腿的发源地。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa7(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 胡安告诉记者，火腿师一般要在学校里学一年的基本理论基础，然后才能进行实践。理论课程主要了解猪的骨骼以及肌肉的生长情况，由于猪的品种不同，肌肉和骨骼的构成也不一样，所以一定在摸清品种之后方可下刀。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 胡安说，火腿的好坏主要取决于原材料：猪。最好的火腿用猪是西班牙人用野猪和家猪交配而成，颜色为黑色，而且越黑越好。此外，猪的养殖也是一门大学问。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa9.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 要制作火腿的猪，必须在野外养殖，这种猪最喜欢吃一种叫&ldquo;佩瑶塔&rdquo;的果实，凡是吃这种果实长大的猪，脂肪的颜色为白色，其胆固醇含量几乎是零。被用于腌制火腿的猪只采用后腿，一般需要腌制8个月到36个月，腌制的时间越长，鲜味越浓。<!--page--></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa10.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 切刀可以说是火腿师的重要工具，高级师傅一般自己要配备七八把之多。什么品种的猪，什么部位的肉，什么时间的肉，采用的切刀都不一样，如果事先不慎重查看，一刀下去切断或者切破肉片，那考试就得扣除很多分数，甚至不及格。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa11(1).jpg\" width=\"599\" height=\"476\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;按照常规，火腿师要把火腿割成一片片薄到不能再薄的程度，但是又要考虑火腿截面的尺寸，不能切断，也不能中间出现空洞。要掌握这个技巧看似容易，但实际操作就不是一回事了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa12.jpg\" width=\"290\" height=\"400\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 像胡安这样的高级师傅，不固定在某一家宾馆内工作，而是在各大饭店走穴。凡是胡安出场切火腿时，主办单位要特意介绍，然后再请他进行&ldquo;表演&rdquo;。胡安先是为客人介绍他将要切割火腿的原料猪的品种，被宰杀的年龄和腌制的年份。然后他用双手切出一些，请客人随意挑出几片，然后比较大小，在客人确认几乎一样大小后，现场常常爆发出热烈的掌声。<!--page--></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa13.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 客人在看他的表演后个个兴高采烈，胃口大增。胡安称高级火腿师可是西班牙的国宝，可以和皇马俱乐部的劳尔媲美，只不过偶尔用脚，他们用手。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa14.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/aa15.jpg\" width=\"599\" height=\"449\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">西班牙火腿要存放3年左右才能食用</span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1364946400', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('275', '18', '蜂蜜采收全过程', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1、先是庭院内紧凑的蜂箱布置，也将是我们的工作场所。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq1(3).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">2、图中的是意大利蜜蜂蜂箱。蜜蜂正在正常出勤，把采集到的花蜜储存在蜜囊内再飞回巢中。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq2(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3、时机成熟时咱们就准备工具收蜜啦！从左边起分别是：蜂帽、搬运蜜脾的箱子、喷壶、起刮刀、蜂刷、割腊刀，另外，还要有胶手套。作用等大家看过都会清楚了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq3(3).jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"538\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4、开始动工！由于意大利蜜蜂常采集蜂胶，并习惯用蜂胶把巢里的缝隙都粘得牢固结实，一般用手去掀开或移动都是有点难度的，所以就要用起刮刀将蜂箱副盖撬开。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq4(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">5、再掀开（起保温保湿作用）的覆布。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq5(2).jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"538\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">6、呵呵！看见了没？都是在忙碌的蜜蜂啊！那些白色的就是蜜蜂在24&mdash;48小时内用刚分泌出来的新蜂蜡筑成的蜂巢，目的是为了有空间储存更多的蜂蜜！而巢框上面的那个铁丝圈，是用来囚禁蜂王的小铁笼，蜂王就在里面，因为蜂群在实行无卵化生产嘛！委屈她了！</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq6(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">7、想给她来个特写的，由于照相技术不好，结果还是看不到了，晕啊！</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq7(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">8、补上一张以前拍的算了，以饱大家眼福！:）不过，需要说明的是：左下角那只是工蜂，负责采集、哺育、和防卫工作；右上角胖胖的那只是雄蜂，只负责跟蜂王交尾！平时就没事到处逛，纯粹一个游手好闲的家伙，多了没用；体形最长的那只就是蜂王啦！专门负责产卵的，所以呢！整箱蜂都有可能都是她的孩子！</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq8(3).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">9、好了！回到采收现场，先把多余的赘脾（蜜蜂的违章建筑）用刀割掉，目的为了方便生产操作。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq9(2).jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"538\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">10、暂时放在一旁的赘脾。可以清晰得看到上面已经开始储蜜了。连脾带蜜一整块都是可以放进嘴里嚼吃的。因为是刚采集回来的花蜜，所以不象成熟蜂蜜那样地甜腻，却很芳香清甜，加上新鲜蜂蜡所独具的嚼头，所以往往成了邻居家小孩们的抢手货，听他们说，放进冰箱冷冻过后口味会更爽，呵呵！不知大家试过没？</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq10(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">11、接着抽出其中的一张蜜脾</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq11(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">12、抖掉上面的蜜蜂，顽固不化者就用蜂刷伺候！</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq12(2).jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"538\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">13、直到刷成这样才行！这时可以看到整张脾上都储满了蜂蜜！而左上部已经出现的封盖痕迹则说明了这张蜜脾的蜜质是成熟的。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq13(2).jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"538\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">14、不断地抽出一张张来。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq14(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">15、然后用搬运箱全部搬到室内，用割蜜刀割掉蜜盖。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq15(3).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">16、之后把蜜脾放进摇蜜桶，利用离心作用把蜂蜜筛出来。为防止金属污染，整个摇蜜桶先用油漆刷过，再用热溶蜂蜡厚厚地包裹起来。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq16(3).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">17、过滤后倒出来，装进干净的白色塑料食品桶中。把摇过的蜜脾取出并放回蜂箱中，恢复原状，重复采收工作。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq17(1).jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"538\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">18、那么，一张蜜脾一次究竟能产多少蜂蜜呢？我们不妨粗略称一称！随便抽一张未取蜜前的巢脾重量，重四斤六两。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq18(1).jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"538\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">19、取完蜜后再称，忽略割除仅二十克的赘脾外，重一斤一两。前后重量相差三斤五两，也就是取出的</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq19(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">20、我们这也有其它蜂种。这箱是中华蜜蜂（也叫土蜂或山蜂）蜂群，蜜蜂个头相对小点。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq20(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">21、抽出一张脾，发现有成熟封盖蜜，也可以采收了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq21(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">22、抖掉蜜蜂后。黄色部分是产卵哺育区，有蜂蛹在内，那是不实行囚王停卵采蜜的结果。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq22.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">23、割除蜡质封蜜盖，准备进行筛取，工序同上述一样。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq23.jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"538\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">24、测量筛出蜂蜜的波美度，读数（蜂蜜浸迹处）为41.5度，完全符合采收标准。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq24.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"717\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">25、当蜜桶再装不下这么多蜂蜜时，就倒进大瓷缸里，缸口用塑膜和胶箍扣紧，这样封存得也更长久。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq25.jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"538\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">26、要取出来时就用勺子盛，装入专用小塑料瓶里。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq26.jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"538\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">27、颜色对比，这是在室内的颜色</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq27.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">28、这是在室外的颜色，有点区别。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq28.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qq15(3).jpg\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1364948767', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('276', '17', '2013年4月6日0农药有机肥蔬菜记录', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>结球生菜终于结球了~。</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd1(3).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd2(5).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>3月中旬&mdash;4月中旬是植物抽薹春化时间，看，连奶油生菜都抽薹了~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd3(3).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd4(6).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>话说，这么多土豆，够吃么？</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd5(3).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>豌豆苗，开花咯~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd6(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>话说，这么多苦苣应该不够吃，吃到三分之一左右，要立刻补种意大利苦苣。</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd7(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd29(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>要移栽了~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd8(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>另外2个品种的辣椒终于出苗了~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd9(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>油菜菜心，终于可以吃了~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd10(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>空心菜，爽口的一种蔬菜，快长吧~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd11(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd12(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>玉米也快长~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd13(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>五一应该是可以吃到黄瓜的，哈哈~~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd14(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>蚕豆开花了~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd15(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>秋季比较受欢迎的苋菜，话说，镇江的大家貌似是越红的苋菜，越喜欢？</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd16(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>香菜也出来了~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd18(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>能长出蘑菇的地方，一般土壤都不错~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd35.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>热红油麦菜，油麦菜爱吃的人不多啊~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd19(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>芥蓝，这次会多种，然后适当长粗点再吃！</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd20(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>室外也种了豇豆~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd21(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>葱不少啊~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd22(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>新的伏玉包菜，终于要开始包心了~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd24(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>四季豆，快长~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd25(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>新的豌豆苗，话说，好菜那么多出来，还有人吃豌豆苗么？</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd26(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>西葫芦，补种了，也发出来了，这个是长出来最大的一株</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd28.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>盐水煮毛豆，大爱啊~，快快长~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd30(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd33(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>西红柿，话说，这些可能也不怎么够吃，等适当时候，要继续补种，今年准备持续吃到12月！</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd31(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd32(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>另外一种包菜，也要准备移栽了~，包菜是个非常营养的蔬菜，希望大家能和我一样，持续的吃！</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd34(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>下周六可以点樱桃萝卜了，希望不会因为季节因素，会产生空心，这次种了3个批次，每个批次间隔1周&mdash;2周，应该可以连续承受大家死命点！</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd38.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>茴香，终于冒出来了~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd39.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>木耳菜，还不够啊，要补种~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd40.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>胡萝卜还没发芽出来~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd41.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>但白萝卜已经发芽了~</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd42.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>乡下的天空还是相对好些的！</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd36.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dd37.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1365217567', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('277', '18', '正宗木子店老米酒酿制全过程', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q1(1).jpg\" width=\"469\" height=\"352\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">原材料：糯米，水，酒药 （酒邱[土话]）<font style=\"COLOR: #fff; FONT-SIZE: 0px\">+ `3 [6 S. O+ S\'  w&amp; V</font><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"display: none;\">5 B2 L/ g9 ~: b9  m</span>糯米浸水<span class=\"t_tag\" href=\"tag.php?name=%CA%B1%BC%E4\">时间</span>：碾和剥分别为1和3天。<font style=\"COLOR: #fff; FONT-SIZE: 0px\">: H</font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q2(1).jpg\" width=\"469\" height=\"352\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">将糯米蒸熟，【闻到香味后蒸10分钟。】 <font style=\"COLOR: #fff; FONT-SIZE: 0px\">3 I! u0 L! N</font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q3(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">熟了，抬倒木桶架上，准备冲水。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q4(1).jpg\" width=\"552\" height=\"414\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">尝点糯米饭。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q5(1).jpg\" width=\"552\" height=\"414\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">冲水。气温高4桶左右，气温低2桶左右，其中一桶必须漫过糯米饭<font style=\"COLOR: #fff; FONT-SIZE: 0px\">6 O0 j.  E2 [% F4。。。。</font><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q6(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">抬下木架，降温。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q7(1).jpg\" width=\"469\" height=\"352\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">温度降低到38度左右伴入酒药。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q8(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">装入木桶。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q9(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">冬季必须这样保温发酵，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q10.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3至7天后，第一次发酵完成，可以舀到酒母（胡子【土话】）了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q11.jpg\" width=\"552\" height=\"414\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">掺水：一般每斤米掺一斤水，如果想长期保存则每斤谷掺一斤水。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q12.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3天后，发酵后的糯米全部泡开了，下一步：榨酒。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q13.jpg\" width=\"469\" height=\"352\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">榨酒。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q14.jpg\" width=\"469\" height=\"352\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">原酒，甜的。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q15.jpg\" width=\"469\" height=\"352\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">装坛，近5天不能密封，这个过程交定浊，到坛子里没有气泡和声音才可密封。用纸板挡住灰尘即可。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/q16.jpg\" width=\"469\" height=\"352\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">酒渣，拌入水酒同量酒药，第二次发酵后，【10天左右】蒸馏出来的就是纯正的米烧酒。</span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1365275696', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('278', '18', '解密传统人工榨清香茶油全过程', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e1(1).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">这个是油茶子。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e2(1).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">油茶子磨出来的粉子。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e3(1).jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">把磨出来的油茶粉子放在锅内蒸熟&sbquo;蒸的火候是出油的关键。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e4(1).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">这是原始的木榨。<br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e5(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">做枯饼用的铁圈。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e6(1).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"473\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">油榨的舱体&sbquo;油就是从这里流下去的。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e7(1).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"487\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;工<span style=\"font-size: small;\">人正在清理油榨的舱体。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e8(3).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">开始用蒸过的稻草做枯饼。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e9(1).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">油茶粉子已经出锅了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e10(1).jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">要装油茶粉子了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e11(2).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">装粉做枯饼。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e12(1).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"512\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">全部装完&sbquo;旁边是做好了的枯饼。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e13(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">将做好了的枯饼放入油榨的舱体。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e14(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">整理上舱的枯饼。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e15(1).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">榨油正式开始了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e16(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;工<span style=\"font-size: small;\">人们用撞杆撞击油榨的销子。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e17.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">枯饼开始出油了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e18(1).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">流出了清香的茶油。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/e19(1).jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">以上就是大山里传统的人工榨油方式的全过程，现在是高效榨油机器替代了这种方式，人工榨油已经稀少了。</span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1365283167', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('279', '18', '茶叶的制作过程', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss1(4).jpg\" width=\"814\" height=\"597\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">刚刚采下的嫩叶。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss2(4).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">照片作者充当了一下手模。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss3(3).jpg\" width=\"789\" height=\"586\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">锅边的嫩芽。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss4(2).jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"629\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">第一道工序，杀青。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss5(2).jpg\" width=\"734\" height=\"560\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">照片作者烧的火。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss6(2).jpg\" width=\"459\" height=\"496\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">杀青之后，就是揉茶。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss7(3).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">接着入锅翻制。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss8(2).jpg\" width=\"557\" height=\"388\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss9(3).jpg\" width=\"658\" height=\"472\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss10(2).jpg\" width=\"858\" height=\"570\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">茶有些变色了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss12(2).jpg\" width=\"734\" height=\"499\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss14(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">这个时候很远就能闻到茶香了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss15(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss16(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">快可以完成做茶了。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ss17(2).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">入锅出锅要揉搓几道，整个过程大概一个半小时。大功告成。</span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1365284525', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('280', '18', '教你认认,野菜大全', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;野菜已被人们视为一种理想的药食兼优的佳蔬，有&ldquo;天然保健食品&rdquo;之美誉。细心的你来认识一下吧。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\r\n<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\">   富国菜即食叶番薯，富含营养，性味甘平，具有健脾胃、益气力等保健作用。可食用部分为其蔓尖嫩茎叶，风味脆嫩甜美，具有清热解毒和滋肾润肺的功效。 </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\r\n<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">五指山野菜又名树仔菜，原产于五指山腹地，集山野之灵气，成为独具风味的纯天然高档菜品。其嫩芽香脆可口，野香十足，碧绿袭人，其营养成分丰富而复杂，具有极高的营养保健价值和独特的药用价值。 </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\r\n<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z3.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"405\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">   马齿苋富含粗蛋白、粗脂肪、粗纤维，以及矿物质钾等多种维生素，有清热解毒、泻热散淤、消肿止痛、平肝除湿、利尿润肺、止渴生津等功效。可营养上皮组织，增强视网膜的感光性，能促进口腔、胃及十二指肠的溃疡愈合。马齿苋还是治疗痢疾和肠炎的良药。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\r\n<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z4.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"365\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong sizcache012195940669878996=\"1\" sizset=\"4\">   </strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">魔芋其主要成分为甘聚糖、蛋白质、果糖、果胶、魔芋淀粉等。能阻碍包括致癌物质在内的有害物质的侵袭，从而起到解毒、防治癌肿的作用，如甲状腺癌、胃贲门癌、结肠癌、淋巴瘤、腮腺癌、鼻咽癌等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z5.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"411\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">   鱼腥草亦称折耳根。通过实验将鱼腥草用于小鼠艾氏腹水癌，有明显抑制作用，对癌细胞分裂最高抑制率为45.7％，可防治胃癌、贲门癌、肺癌等。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\r\n<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z6.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"373\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">车前草常见的有两种：具有主根的为平车前，又名小车前，不具有主根的为车前。车前草有清热利尿、明目、祛痰功能。主治小便不通、咳嗽、多痰、尿血。嫩叶用开水烫后食用，对治疗尿路感染、水肿、高血压均有疗效，常服无毒副作用。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z7.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"819\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">   莼菜其主要成分为氨基酸、天门冬素、岩藻糖、阿拉伯糖、果糖等。莼菜叶背的分泌物对某些转移性肿瘤有抑制作用。可防治胃癌、前列腺癌等多种肿瘤。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong sizcache012195940669878996=\"1\" sizset=\"7\"> <br />\r\n<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">人参菜食用嫩梢，宜炒食或作汤，对糖尿病有一定疗效，煎液可治疗红眼病。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong sizcache012195940669878996=\"1\" sizset=\"8\"> <br />\r\n<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z9.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"418\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z10.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"409\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">黄秋葵嫩荚可用来炒食、作汤、凉拌，有治疗胃炎、胃溃疡及痔瘘的功效。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong sizcache012195940669878996=\"1\" sizset=\"10\"> <br />\r\n<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z11.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">香麻叶叶作蔬菜用，味甘甜，具有清热凉血之功效，宜炒食、作汤或火锅。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z12.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"415\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">   紫背菜食用嫩梢，叶片润滑、茎部爽口，具有补血、消炎、治疗经痛、血气亏、支气管炎等功效。炒食拌入腐乳、沙茶酱等作料，则独具风味。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\r\n<strong sizcache012195940669878996=\"1\" sizset=\"12\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z13.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z14.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"380\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">罗勒药用和食用，健胃，促进消化，利尿强心。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong sizcache012195940669878996=\"1\" sizset=\"14\"> <br />\r\n<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z15.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">紫苏用作蔬菜或入茶。叶有解表散寒、行气和胃功效。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> <img src=\"/images/upload/Image/z16.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"362\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">  蒲公英其主要成分为蒲公英素、蒲公英甾醇、蒲公英苦素、果胶、菊糖、胆硷等。可防治肺癌、胃癌、食管癌及多种肿瘤。 <br />\r\n过敏体质不宜食用。平常服止痛药、磺胺药或吃某些食物、接触某些物质易发生过敏者，采食野菜应慎重。首次应少量食用，食后如出现周身发痒、浮肿、皮疹或皮下出血等过敏或中毒症状，应停食野菜，并到医院诊治，以免引起对肝、肾功能的损害。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">   另外，许多野菜，如野苋菜、柳树芽、野苜蓿和臭椿等，食用前必须用开水烫，再用清水漂洗几次，沥去苦水，方可烧煮食用；采摘野菜时一定要分辨清楚，野菜不宜久存，要吃新鲜为好。</span></p>', '', '', '', '0', '1', '1365446219', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('282', '17', '2013年4月10日0农药有机肥蔬菜记录', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">感觉这次的樱桃萝卜不如以往的红，看来种子需要再调节一下，开拓者F1的应该是最好的。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f1(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">芝麻菜，开始长大了~，我没吃过。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f2(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">茴香，比上次看到的大了点了，是不是还要再种点。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f3(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">绕过了抽薹季节，紫青菜再过一周左右，可以吃了。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f4(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f29.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">小青菜，这时候是最好吃的啊。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">苦苣的生长周期还是比较长的，这次让它长大点吃。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f6.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">油菜菜心，都有一些开花了~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f7.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">空心菜，长大了不少啊~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f8.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f9.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">玉米也是~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f10.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">黄瓜周末要搭黄瓜架子了~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f11.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f12.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">苋菜再过阵子，就要移栽了~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f13.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">话说，这是啥玩意，我也记不得了，另外一个品种的苋菜？</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f14.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f15.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">鸡毛菜，快好吃了~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f16.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">长杆茼蒿，长出来了~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f17.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">红热油麦菜，终于长大了。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f18.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">荷兰豆啊，切丝清炒，一级棒啊</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f19.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f20.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">露天也种了一批豇豆。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f21.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">笋瓜，不知道味道咋样~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f22.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">四季豆都有一些开花了~，快咯快咯~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f23.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">新发了一小部分豌豆苗，再来一周就开吃吧~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f24.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">冰心紫荷，卖相很不错。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f25.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">西红柿，生命力顽强。就是土比较瘦，后期追肥有的追了~</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f26.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">毛豆又大了点了，这个可以固氮，可以起到改良土壤的作用。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f27.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">茄子苗终于立起来了。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/f28.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></span></strong></span></p>', '', '', '', '1', '1', '1365541112', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('281', '18', '奶酪制作全过程：访意大利传统干酪厂', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这是意大利一家生产<strong>Grana Padano</strong>干酪的工厂，Grana Padano干酪受到原产地命名保护（PDO），必须在原产地按照传统方式生产，否则不能标上Grana Padano的标签。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s1(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>1.</strong> 牛奶被注入传统的奶酪槽，奶酪槽表面是铜制的，铜是最好的导热材料。如今，使用这种传统的铜制奶酪槽需要经过相关部门的特殊批准，因为现在的法规限制食品与铜制材料接触。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s2.jpg\" width=\"340\" height=\"255\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>2.</strong> 牛奶和利用乳清制作的发酵液被加热到31-33℃。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>3.</strong> 凝乳酶经过稀释后，被加入牛奶中。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>4.</strong> 大约15 min后，牛奶凝固。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s5(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>5.</strong> 用特制的工具，手工切割凝乳。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>6.</strong> 检查凝乳颗粒的大小，凝乳颗粒切割的越小，干酪越硬。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s7.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>7.</strong> 温度被提高到56℃，进行高温热煮，这个过程中更多乳清会从凝乳颗粒中析出。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s8.jpg\" width=\"340\" height=\"255\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>8.</strong> 经过30-70 min，凝乳颗粒逐渐下沉并融合。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s9.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>9.</strong>用杠杆将奶酪从奶酪槽底部挑起来。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s10.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>10.</strong> 用麻布包住奶酪。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s11.jpg\" width=\"340\" height=\"255\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>11.</strong> 随后，包裹奶酪的麻布被系在奶酪槽上的一根横杆上。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s12.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>12.</strong> 凝乳被平分为两块。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s13.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>13.</strong> 两块凝乳用麻布分别包裹起来。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s14.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>14.</strong> 凝乳被放入酸性液体短暂浸泡。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s15.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>15.</strong> 随后，凝乳被放入Teflon模具，凝乳上贴了一块用酪蛋白制作的标签。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s16.jpg\" width=\"340\" height=\"255\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>16.</strong> 奶酪这样放置约8小时，在重物挤压下更多乳清析出。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s17.jpg\" width=\"340\" height=\"255\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>17.</strong> 之后，奶酪被放入这种金属模具，放置24小时。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s18.jpg\" width=\"255\" height=\"340\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>18.</strong> 奶酪被成批放入盐渍池。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s19.jpg\" width=\"340\" height=\"255\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>19.</strong> 经过盐渍后，奶酪在一个温暖环境下干燥。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s20.jpg\" width=\"340\" height=\"255\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>20.</strong> 奶酪干燥后，就被放入恒温恒湿的成熟室，Grana Padano奶酪至少要成熟9个月。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s21.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>21.</strong> 壮观的奶酪成熟室。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/s22.jpg\" width=\"510\" height=\"383\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>22.</strong> 一只切开的Grana Padano奶酪。</span></p>', '', '', '', '1', '1', '1365450452', '', '0', 'http://', '');
