\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">2、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">3、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">李家&ldquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span>农药有机肥&rdquo;蔬菜二人单月套餐：</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/2ren1.jpg\" width=\"760\" height=\"230\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>配送箱实物图：</strong></u></span></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/0nong.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">注：</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）配送时间：每周三、六配送。<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><u>蔬菜的采摘在当日早晨<span lang=\"EN-US\">6-7</span>点，下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">2-5</span>点间配送到各个领菜点</u></strong></span>。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）配送箱：每户家庭配备了<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>个配送箱，防止蔬菜水分蒸发和运输过程中的挤压。可以选择每次将箱子带回家，下次领菜的时候还到领菜点，也可以选择不带走箱子，每次带方便袋来取走菜。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>）套餐选菜方式：农场会<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>固定<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>种</strong></u></span>多数人较为喜欢的蔬菜，剩余的品种自由选择。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有特殊要求的可联系客服。</span></strong></u></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）</span><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">过敏性反应：<u>若是对某些科属的蔬菜有过敏性反应的，例如化学物质过敏体质，对十字花科类蔬菜均过敏的，提前告知我们。</u></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong>5、原味生活的创新：选择自由的会员制套餐配置系统</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;以下为会员操作界面截图：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/2(1).jpg\" width=\"789\" height=\"666\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">详细的订餐操作过程，请参照网页下方的</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://yw0511.com/article-179.html\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>&ldquo;</strong></u></span><u style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>蔬菜</strong></u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>套餐操作界面解说&rdquo;</strong></u></span></a>。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/2(2).jpg\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>', 'images/201211/thumb_img/47_thumb_G_1353958908590.jpg', 'images/201211/goods_img/47_G_1353958908653.jpg', 'images/201211/source_img/47_G_1353958908418.png', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1350691208', '10', '0', '1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1362369168', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('111', '9', 'ljf031', '“李家”紫青菜', '+strong', '142', '21', '', '10', '0.5', '9.60', '8.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '紫青菜口味和小青菜一样，但含有丰富的青花素，对身体很好，属于高档菜。', '<p>&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#FF6600\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#FF6600\">、简介：</span></strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: small; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">（下图为实物图）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/zi1.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">紫青菜和青菜一样，是十字花科芸薹属的叶用蔬菜，学名<span lang=\"EN-US\">Brassica chinensis var chinensis</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#FF6600\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#FF6600\">、紫青菜的食疗作用：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">紫色青菜的叶子是紫色的，但是茎还是绿色的。紫色青菜虽然食用起来的口感跟普通的青菜差不多，但是营养成分却是天差地别，其叶子中<strong><u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">含有花青素，是一种强有力的抗氧化剂，可以预防癌症、心脏病、中风、关节炎等多种疾病，并能延缓衰老、有益健康，比普通青菜营养价值更高</span></u></strong>。这种紫色青菜其中所含的营养成分和紫甘蓝几乎相同，由于紫甘蓝不适合夏季的气候条件，因此市场上<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>缺位<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>而紫色青菜正好可以给喜欢紫甘蓝的市民找到一个很好的替代品。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">4、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">5、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;紫</span>青菜寄语：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">高档蔬菜之一&mdash;&mdash;含有丰富的钙、铁和维生素C、胡萝卜素也很丰富，是人体黏膜及上皮组织维持生长的重要营养源，对于抵御皮肤过度角化大有裨益。爱美人士不妨多吃一些油菜，一定会收到意想不到的美容效果。</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">6、保存方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>若是紫青菜表面有水，则先把菜表面的水滴风干掉，然后放入袋子，一定记得放一张纸巾进去，在冰箱冷藏保存的时候，纸巾会吸附一些水气。这样，菜叶和菜梗儿就不会被湿漉漉的水分浸泡，也就不会腐烂，保存时间会就延长。若是紫青菜表面没水，则放入保鲜袋冷藏保存即可。</span></p>', 'images/201302/thumb_img/111_thumb_G_1359757568738.jpg', 'images/201302/goods_img/111_G_1359757568508.jpg', 'images/201302/source_img/111_G_1359757568677.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1354486855', '100', '0', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '1363732958', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
