 color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、极品罗莎生菜的营养价值：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">罗莎生菜茎叶中含有</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">莴苣</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">素，故味微苦，具有镇痛催眠、降低胆固醇、辅助治疗神经衰弱等功效；罗莎生菜中含有甘露醇等有效成分，有利尿和促进血液循环的作用。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">罗莎生菜中含有一种&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">干扰素</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">诱生剂&rdquo;，可刺激人体正常细胞产生干扰素，从而产生一种&ldquo;抗病毒蛋白&rdquo;抑制病毒。具有清热安神、清肝利胆、</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">养胃</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">的功效。适宜</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">胃病</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">、维生素C缺乏者；适宜肥胖、减肥者；适宜高</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">胆固醇</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">、神经衰弱者、</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">肝胆病</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">患者食用；生食、常食可有利于女性保持苗条的身材。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p cl