t-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">由于花椰菜的含水量高达<span lang=\"EN-US\">90%</span>以上，所含热量较低（每杯<span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">32</span>千卡）</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，因此对希望减肥的人来说，它可以填饱肚子，而不会使你发胖。与其他大多数甘蓝品种比较，白色的花椰菜含有低量的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>。每一杯（<span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span>毫升）熟菜花食品提供的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>相当于一个中等大小的桔子所含的量。生的花椰菜与煮熟的相比较，至少能够多提供<span lang=\"EN-US\">20%</span>以上的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>。花椰菜营养丰富，含有蛋白质、脂肪、磷、铁、胡萝卜素、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B1</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B2</span>和维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>等，尤以维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>丰富，每<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/74027.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; text-decoration: initial;\">克</span></span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">含<span lang=\"EN-US\">88</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">毫克，仅次于辣椒，是蔬菜中含量最高的一种。其质地细嫩，味甘鲜美，容易消化，对保护血液有益。儿童食用有利健康成长。但西蓝花小孩不能多吃，因为它里面含有一种有害化学物质叫异硫氰酸烯丙酯（芥末油的主要成分）。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">菜花的含水量高达<span lang=\"EN-US\">90%</span>以上，而</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">热量较低，每杯（<span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span>毫升）仅<span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">32</span>千卡，因此，对对于希望减肥的人来说，它既可以填饱肚子，而又不会使人发胖。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、花菜水煮或凉拌营养价值更高：</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small; text-indent: 12pt;\">&nbsp; 花菜是一种很受人们欢迎的蔬菜，它味道鲜美，营养也很高，还有很高的药用价值。它的维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small; text-indent: 12pt;\">C</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small; text-indent: 12pt;\">含量非常丰富，它比辣椒的含量都高很多。它还具有抗癌功效，其功效已经被全世界人认可，西兰花的平均营养价值及防病作用远远超出其他蔬菜，名列第一。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/shanghuilijianfeng.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" alt=\"\" /></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">&nbsp; &ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">再安全的东西不好吃也不能持久！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>所以在好吃上，我下了功夫，主要从两方面，一品种、二有机肥。希望您尝尝看，缺点请多指正！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>花菜寄语：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">吃起来很嫩，样子也很漂亮。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、保存方法：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">用保鲜膜包好不漏气，放冰箱保鲜上，一般能放一周以上。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201211/thumb_img/91_thumb_G_1353871325655.jpg', 'images/201211/goods_img/91_G_1353871325050.jpg', 'images/201211/source_img/91_G_1353871325126.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1352240705', '100', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1361398706', '11', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('93', '11', 'ljf017', '“李家”莴苣', '+strong', '72', '21', '', '10', '0.5', '9.60', '8.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '莴苣杆子略细，切切丝清炒肉丝，口味不错！', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、简介：</span></strong></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: small; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">（下图为实物图）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ee4.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">莴苣，菊科，莴苣属，一、二年生草本植物。莴苣可分为叶用和茎用两类。莴苣的名称很多，在本草书上称作</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">千金菜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">莴苣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">石苣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">。叶用莴苣又称春菜、生菜，茎用莴苣又称莴笋、香笋。我国各地栽培面积莴笋比生菜多。莴笋的肉质嫩，茎可生食、凉拌、炒食、干制或腌渍。生菜主要食叶片或叶球，近年来在各大城市尤其是南方沿海各省的大城市有所发展，成为当前增加花式品种的主要蔬菜。莴苣茎叶中含有莴苣素，味苦，高温干旱苦味浓，能增强胃液，刺激消化，增进食欲，并具有镇痛和催眠的作用。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></strong></span></span><strong style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">莴苣的食疗作用：</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">止腹痛</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 6pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">儿童们腹部受了寒冷，或者成年人受到风寒，腹部隐隐作痛。如果不喜欢吃药，那么可将莴苣的茎和叶，捣烂后放在锅炉上煮熟，作为饮品，能止腹痛。因为莴苣笋的茎叶中，有一种白 色的乳状液，名为莴亚片，英文名称为<span lang=\"EN-US\">LACTUCAIUM</span>。据药学家的研究，说这种液汁，有镇痛和麻醉之效，有一种新药即有乳状液的成分。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 6pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">止牙血</span></strong></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　凡是身体虚弱，阴分不足，齿缝间时常出血，或鼻部干燥，易出鼻血。均可用莴苣茎切片煮熟加酱油或盐拌食，以治疗和减少出血情况。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通小便</span></span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small; text-indent: 12pt;\">小儿小便不便时，可用莴苣茎和叶，捣烂如泥，涂敷肚脐之上，小便可以渐渐通畅，此法载在卫生简易方中。又有一个办法，用葱数十茎，与莴苣茎十茎一同捣烂，加蜜糖或甘油调成泥饼状，涂在脐眼以上的肚腹部，亦能使小便通畅。涂敷时有一要点，就是莴苣的泥饼要用热水温热，再行涂上，免得受冷。敷布的位置，要离开脐眼，敷在肚上。或预先用棉花或纱布填塞脐眼，免得液汁浸入，那么就更妥善了</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、食用禁忌：</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）不可多食，多食使人目糊，李时珍引彭乘语云：莴苣 有毒，百虫不敢近，蛇虺触之，则目瞑不见物，人中其毒，以姜汁解之。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）不宜与奶酪、蜂蜜同食。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>）寒性体质者不宜食。</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）痛风、泌尿道结石，眼疾患者不宜食。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>莴苣寄语：</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">莴苣杆子，切切丝清炒肉丝，口味不错！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、保存方法：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">把蔬菜的腐烂部分摘除，放进塑料袋内，把袋口扎紧，置于阴凉干燥之处。</span></p>', 'images/201