 align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）增强机体免疫功能：萝卜含丰富的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>和微量元素锌，有助于增强机体的免疫功能，提高抗病能力</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）帮助消化：萝卜中的芥子油能促进胃肠蠕动，增加食欲，帮助消化；</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）帮助营养物质的吸收：萝卜中的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">淀粉酶能分解食物中的淀粉、脂肪、使之得到充分的吸收</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）防癌抗癌：萝卜含有木质素，能提高</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">巨噬细胞的活力，吞噬癌细胞。此外，萝卜所含的多种酶，能分解致癌的亚硝酸胺，具有防癌作用。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、搭配宜忌：</span></strong></span><a name=\"ref_[1]_30729\"></a><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#FF6600\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=