ze: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>白萝卜寄语：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">一烧就烂，是这个萝卜的特点，孩子的大爱<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\">~</span></span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、保存方法：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">把买回来的白萝卜在阳台上晾一个晚上，等表皮起皱后装进密封袋，即可防止水分的流失。这样保存白萝卜一个月也不会空心。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201211/thumb_img/96_thumb_G_1353871276960.jpg', 'images/201211/goods_img/96_G_1353871276947.jpg', 'images/201211/source_img/96_G_1353871276366.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1354516269', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1361398716', '11', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
