g><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、油麦菜的食疗作用：</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">油麦菜含有大量维生素和大量钙、铁、蛋白质、脂肪、维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">A</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">VB1</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">VB2</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">等营养成分，是生食蔬菜中的上品，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">凤尾</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">之称</span></strong></u></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">。油麦菜具有降低胆固醇、治疗神经衰弱、清燥润肺、化痰止咳等功效，是一种低热量、高营养的蔬菜。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、注意事项：</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　</span><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">胃炎，泌尿系统疾病</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，性质寒凉，尿频、胃寒的人应少吃</span></span></strong></u><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p 