font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">紫甘蓝的营养丰富，尤以丰富的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、较多的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>和维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>族，以及丰富的花青素甙和纤维素等，备受人们的欢迎。主要营养成分与结球甘蓝差不多，每<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>克食用部分含含胡萝卜素<span lang=\"EN-US\">0.11</span>毫克、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B1 0.04</span>毫克、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B2 0.04</span>毫克、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C 39</span>毫克、尼克酸<span lang=\"EN-US\">0.3</span>毫克、糖类<span lang=\"EN-US\">4%</span>、蛋白质<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.3%</span>、脂肪<span lang=\"EN-US\">0.3%</span>、粗纤维<span lang=\"EN-US\">0.9%</span>、钙<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>毫克、磷<span lang=\"EN-US\">56</span>毫克、铁<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.9</span>毫克。其中含有的维生素成分及矿物质都高于结球甘蓝。所以公认紫甘蓝的营养价值高于结球甘蓝。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;【食疗作用】：</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span>克甘蓝菜中所含有的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>的数量是一个柑橘的两倍。此外，这种蔬菜还能够给人体提供一定数量的具有重要作用的抗氧化剂：维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>与维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>前身物质<span lang=\"EN-US\">(&beta;―</span>胡萝卜<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>，这些抗氧化成分能够保护身体免受自由基的损伤，并能有助于细胞的更新。它有强身健体的作用，经常食用能够增强人的活力。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　甘蓝菜是一类强身健体的蔬菜。紫甘蓝含有丰富的硫元素，这种元素的主要作用是杀虫止痒，对于各种皮肤瘙痒，湿疹等疾患具有一定疗效，因而经常吃这类蔬菜对于维护皮肤健康十分有益。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　凡是经常吃甘蓝蔬菜的人，都能轻而易举地满足机体对纤维素的需求。这类蔬菜中含有的大量纤维素，能够增强胃肠功能，促进肠道蠕动，以及降低胆固醇水平。此外，经常吃甘蓝蔬菜还能够防治过敏症，因此皮肤过敏的人最好把甘蓝视为一道保留菜。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　其中的铁元素，能够提高血液中氧气的含量，有助于机体对脂肪的燃烧，从而对于减肥大有裨益。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 甘蓝类蔬菜同药物一样，能够减轻关节疼痛症状，并且还能够防治感冒引起的咽喉疼痛。因此，关节炎患者最好经常吃这类蔬菜，并且为了防止感冒引起的咽喉部炎症，在冬春季节感冒的高发季节，也应当经常吃甘蓝菜。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、包菜和紫包菜哪个更营养：</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><font size=\"2\">&nbsp; 包菜和紫包菜，是日常人们爱吃的蔬菜，而人们也会疑惑，这两种模样一致、颜色不同的菜到底有什么区别。</font></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 包菜，也被称球甘蓝、圆白菜，别名卷心菜，属于甘蓝的变种。世界卫生组织推荐的最佳食物中，卷心菜排名第三。卷心菜营养相当丰富，含有大量的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，纤维素以及碳水化合物及各种矿物质，多吃卷心菜有防癌功效。卷心菜新鲜汁液能治疗胃和十二指溃疡，有止痛及促进愈合作用。紫包菜也叫紫甘蓝，叶片紫红，叶面有蜡粉，叶球近圆形。营养丰富，尤其含有丰富的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>和维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>族。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 专家表示，两者同属甘蓝的不同品种，在营养成分上，卷心菜和紫甘蓝没有太大的差别，但相对于卷心菜来说，紫甘蓝还含有丰富的花青素，它是一种强有力的抗氧化剂，它能够保护人体免受自由基的损伤，有抗衰老的作用。还能增强血管弹性，抑制炎症和过敏，改善关节的柔韧性。此外，紫甘蓝具有特殊的香气和风味，可煮、炒食、凉拌或作泡菜等，因含丰富的色素，是拌色拉或西餐配色的好原料。在炒或煮紫甘蓝时，在操作前，加少许白醋，否则，经加热后就会变成黑紫色。而卷心菜适于炒、炝等，可与番茄一起做汤，也可作馅心。 卷心菜能抑制癌细胞，通常秋天种植的卷心菜抑制率较高，因此秋冬时期的卷心菜可以多吃。购买时不宜多，以免搁几天后，减少营养成分。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/shanghuilijianfeng.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red\">&nbsp; &ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red\">再安全的东西不好吃也不能持久！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>所以在好吃上，我下了功夫，主要从两方面，一品种、二有机肥。希望您尝尝看，缺点请多指正！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>紫包菜寄语：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">在寒冬中成长起来的紫包菜，浓缩了植物的糖分，切成丝、炒个糖醋紫包菜，让全家人的味蕾绽放起来<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\">~</span></span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、保存方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将紫包菜放入保鲜袋，再放到冰箱冷藏室保存，尽早食用。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201211/thumb_img/101_thumb_G_1353871221328.jpg', 'images/201211/goods_img/101_G_1353871221111.jpg', 'images/201211/source_img/101_G_1353871221217.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1352241027', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1361398769', '0', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('102', '9', 'ljf008', '“李家”大白菜', '+strong', '94', '21', '', '10', '3.0', '57.59', '48.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '外面的大白菜都是吃起来完全没味道，同时大白菜也是市场上使用农药等最多的菜之一，不妨试试这种种植方式种出来的，看看区别呢？', '<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、简介：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">（下图为实物图）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/dabaicai.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">白菜原产于我国北方，是十字花科芸薹属叶用蔬菜，通常指大白菜；也包括小白菜以及由甘蓝的栽培变种结球甘蓝，即<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>圆白菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>或<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>洋白菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。引种南方，南北各地均有栽培。十九世纪传入日本、欧美各国。白菜种类很多，北方的大白菜有山东胶州大白菜、北京青白、天津青麻叶大白菜、东北大矮白菜、山西阳城的大毛边等。同时白菜作为相关网络用语使用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、大白菜的食疗作用：</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-indent: 12pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">大白菜</span><span style=\"text-indent: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">是一种很常见的蔬菜，它是一种普通的不能再普通的蔬菜，但是它的功能却不能小觑。它营养丰富，含有丰富的</span><span style=\"text-indent: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">粗纤维、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>等，它还具有清热解毒的功效。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　</span></span><u><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">白菜含<span lang=\"EN-US\">90%</span>的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">植物纤维</span></span></strong></u></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>百菜不如白菜，白菜中的凝血止血酶能预防中风，钼还能防癌。白菜的营养很均衡，对身体有好处。白菜里面含有<span lang=\"EN-US\">90%</span>的植物纤维，这些植物纤维能促进胃肠的蠕动，促进消化系统的健康。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>王宜主任说。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　白菜肉包荤素搭配合理</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　王宜主任介绍，<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>白菜肉包<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>非常适合中午和晚上食用，可以选择热吃，也可以晾凉吃。它最大的特点就在于做法的健康和荤素搭配的合理。蒸菜最大程度保持了菜中的营养，同时吃肉较多的话，肉类消化后的废弃物排除是一个困难，有些人吃肉会便秘。但是和白菜一起搭配的话，蛋白质被吸收以后，肉类的碎渣在蔬菜的高纤维帮助下可以很顺利地排出体外。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　</span><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">白菜渣滓敷脸可治痤疮</span></span></strong></u></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>白菜可是浑身是宝。做菜时切下来的白菜帮一样是有用的，如果家中有</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">榨汁机的话，可以把白菜帮榨成汁。白菜汁可以加冰糖饮用，也可以在包饺子的时候和面。至于剩下的渣滓，可以捣碎敷在脸上，具有清热、解毒、消炎的功效，对痤疮也有很好的治疗作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>王宜主任说。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">DIY&ldquo;</span>白菜肉包<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　蒸<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>白菜肉包<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>首先选择叶大帮薄的大白菜，和几两很细的肉馅。将白菜帮去掉大部分，接着把白菜叶焯一下后平铺在桌面上，然后按着自己的口味和肉馅，可以在肉馅里面和上一些其他的蔬菜，切碎的豆制品、香菇、木耳等，保证</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">动物蛋白和植物蛋白全面。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">菜品应该吃原汁原味的，就在里面加上一些葱和姜来调味，同时加一些</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">酱油、盐即可。和好了馅以后，把肉馅包在白菜里。包好后开始上屉蒸，大约蒸十五分钟，外面的白菜变色了，里面的肉也熟了即可。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、宜忌事项：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">忌食隔夜的熟白菜和未腌透的大白菜。</span></span></strong></u></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">腹泻者尽量忌食大白菜。</span></span></strong></u></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">气虚胃寒的人忌多吃。</span></span></strong></u></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）切大白菜时，宜顺丝切，这样大白菜易熟。</span></strong></u></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">5、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">6、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>大白菜寄语：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">外面的大白菜都是吃起来完全没味道，同时大白菜也是市场上使用农药等最多的菜之一，不妨试试这种种植方式种出来的，看看区别呢？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">7、保存方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将大白菜码放在阴凉通风的地方，固定一段时间后，上下倒一回，使这些白菜能</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">呼吸</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">顺畅。如果有条件还是尽量将白菜码放在室外或者远离居室的单独房间。</span></span></p>', 'images/201211/thumb_img/102_thumb_G_1353871208500.jpg', 'images/201211/goods_img/102_G_1353871208315.jpg', 'images/201211/source_img/102_G_1353871208404.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1352241053', '100', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1365220363', '0', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('103', '7', 'ljf007', '“李家”西红柿', '+strong', '112', '21', '', '1', '0.5', '9.60', '8.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '自然生长的0农药有机肥的西红柿，可以同时买个超市西红柿，首先切开看看内部的区别，再尝尝，区别不言而喻！', '<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、简介：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">（下图为实物图）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/xi2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">番茄<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Tomato)</span>别名西红柿、洋柿子，古名六月柿、喜报三元。在秘鲁和墨西哥，最初称之为<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>狼桃<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。果实营养丰富，具特殊风味。可以生食、煮食、加工制成番茄酱、汁或整果罐藏。番茄是全世界栽培最为普遍的果菜之一。 美国、苏联、意大利和中国为主要生产国。在欧、美洲的国家、中国和日本有大面积温室、塑料大棚及其他保护地设施栽培。中国各地普遍种植。栽培面积仍在继续扩大。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、西红柿的食疗作用：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">番茄味甘、酸，性凉，微寒。能清热止渴，养阴，凉血，归肝、胃、肺经。具有生津止渴，健胃消食，清热解毒，凉血平肝，补血养血和增进食欲的功效。可治口渴，食欲不振等多种疾病，具体内容如下：</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【治皮肤病】</b></u></span>：将鲜熟西红柿去皮和籽后捣烂敷患处，每日<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>次，可治真菌、感染性皮肤病，效果那是当相当的好，比较合适现在的在校大学生，宅男。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【美容、防衰老】</b></u></span>：将鲜熟西红柿捣烂取汁加少许白糖，每天用其涂面，能使皮肤细腻光滑，美容防衰老效果极佳，女性朋友不可多得的好东西啊，便宜实用，还环保。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><b>【防癌】</b></span></u>：因西红柿不仅营养丰富，且具有较强的清热解毒、抑制病变功效，坚持每天生食<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>个鲜熟的西红柿，可起到防癌和辅助治疗癌症的作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【治高血压】</b></u></span>：每天早晨选<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>个鲜熟西红柿空腹蘸白糖吃，降血压效果明显，这个特别适合中老年人。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<b>　</b><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【治贫血】</b></u></span>：将西红柿、苹果各<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>个，芝麻<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>克，一次吃完，每日吃<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>次，长期坚持，可治贫血，对体质差的女性朋友，还有一些更年期的阿姨有帮助。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【治溃疡】</b></u></span>：轻度消化性溃疡患者，可将榨取的西红柿和马铃薯汁各半杯混合后饮用，每天早晚各一次，连服<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>次，溃疡可愈。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><b>【治肝炎】</b></span></u>：取西红柿丁一匙，芹菜末、胡萝卜末、猪油各半匙，拌入沸粳米粥内烫熟，加入盐、味精适量食用，对治疗肝炎效果极佳。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【防中暑】</b></u></span>：将<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>个西红柿切片，加盐或糖少许，熬汤热饮，可防中暑。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【退高烧】</b></u></span>：将西红柿汁和西瓜汁各半杯混合饮用，每小时饮一次，可退高烧。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【治牙龈出血】</b></u></span>：将西红柿洗净当水果吃，连吃半月，即可治愈牙龈出血。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【降脂降压】</b></u></span>：番茄中含有丰富的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>及<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，其酸性是由于柠檬酸及苹果酸所致，口服番茄果胶，可降低饲胆甾醇大鼠血清及肝中的胆甾醇量。番茄汁可使高血压下降，平滑肌兴奋。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><b>【抗真菌】</b></span></u>：番茄碱有抗真菌作用。能抑制某些对于植物或人有致病力的真菌；但对细菌之效力很差。其抑菌原理可能是在真菌的细胞膜内形成某种甾醇复合物。其甙元（番茄胺）作用很差。最初从番茄中提出的番茄素，其中混有芦丁，特别是其甙元<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>槲皮素；槲皮素能拮抗番茄碱的抗菌作用， 因而番茄素的抗真菌作用不强。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><b>【预防胃癌】</b></span></u>：胃癌，位居全球肿瘤发病和癌症死亡率第<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>位，是危害人们健康的一大杀手。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　在很多世界性卫生组织推荐的抗癌或保健食品中，番茄总是位居前列。意大利研究表明，番茄能抑制胃癌的发生，每周吃<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>次番茄制品的人，比每周仅吃<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>次的胃癌发病危险性降低<span lang=\"EN-US\">50%</span>。日本的研究发现，在随机选择的居民血浆中的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">&beta;</span>胡萝卜素和番茄红素的水平分析中，只有血浆番茄红素与胃癌呈显著负相关。以上的研究均说明番茄红素和番茄制品能显著降低胃癌和食管癌的发病率。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【消炎】</b></u></span>：番茄碱在动物实验申有明显的消炎作用。给大鼠肌肉注射<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 1</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">10mg/kg</span>或口服<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">30mg/kg</span>能显著减轻角叉菜引起的足踝水肿；切除肾上腺后，作用更明显。皮下注射<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">10mg/kg</span>共<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>天，可抑制肉芽组织的形成。对小鼠皮下注射<span lang=\"EN-US\">10mg/kg</span>可降低毛细血管通透性。其甙元无抗炎作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><b>【补血】</b></span></u>：酸奶的蛋白质成分能促进铁的吸收，因此，把西红柿和酸奶搭配在一起榨出的西红柿酸奶汁是提高体内铁元素吸收的良好来源，可有效补血。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【健胃消食，润肠通便】</b></u></span>：所含苹果酸、柠檬酸等有机酸，能促使胃液分泌，对脂肪及蛋白质的消化。增加胃酸浓度，调整胃肠功能，有助胃肠疾病的康复。所含果酸及纤维素，有助消化、润肠通便作用，可防治便秘。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><b>【清热解毒，生津止渴】</b></span></u>：番茄性凉味甘酸，有清热生津、养阴凉血的功效，对发热烦渴、口干舌燥、牙龈出血、胃热口苦、虚火上升有较好治疗效果。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><b>【降脂降压，利尿排钠】</b></span></u>：所含维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、芦丁、番茄红素及果酸，可降低血胆固醇，预防动脉粥样硬化及冠心病。另含有大量的钾及碱性矿物质，能促进血中钠盐的排出，有降压、利尿、消肿作用，对高血压、肾脏病有良好的辅助治疗作用。降低血压经常发生牙龈出血或皮下出血的患者，吃番茄有助于改善症状。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><b>【抗血凝聚，防脑血栓】</b></span></u>：国外研究发现，从番茄籽周围黄色果冻状的汁液中分离出来了一种被称为<span lang=\"EN-US\">P3</span>的物质，具有抗血小板凝聚的功效，可以防止脑血栓的发生。患冠心病及中风的病人每天适量饮用番茄汁有益于病的康复。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【防癌抗癌，延缓衰老】</b></u></span>：近年来，研究证实番茄中所含番茄红素具有独特的抗氧化作用，可清除体内的自由基，预防心血管疾病的发生，有效地减少胰腺癌、直肠癌、口腔癌、乳腺癌的发生，阻止前列腺癌变的进程。番茄还含有防癌抗衰老的谷胱甘肽，可清除体内有毒物质，恢复机体器官正常功能，延缓衰老，故番茄拥有<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">长寿果<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>之美誉。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><b>【防白内障，黄斑变性】</b></span></u>：所含维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，可预防白内障，还对夜盲症有一定防治效果<span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span>番茄红素具有抑制脂质过氧化的作用，能防止自由基的破坏，抑制视网膜黄斑变性，维护视力。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【美容护肤，治皮肤病】</b></u></span>：番茄含胡萝卜素和维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，有祛雀斑、美容、抗衰老、护肤等功效，治真菌、感染性皮肤病。尼克酸能维持胃液的正常分泌，促进红血球的形成，有利于保持血管壁的弹性和保护皮肤<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span>另一项研究显示，番茄汁还对消除狐臭有一定作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><b>【维护性功能】</b></u></span>： 番茄红素具有独特的抗氧化能力，能清除自由基，保护细胞，使脱氧核糖核酸及基因免遭破坏，能阻止癌变进程。吸收后聚集于前列腺、肾上腺等处，促使前列腺液分泌旺盛，可维护射精功能；番茄多汁，可以利尿，肾炎病人也宜食用。女性多吃番茄可激发性欲和激情。番茄除了对前列腺癌有预防作用外，还能有效减少胰腺癌、直肠癌、喉癌、口腔癌、肺癌、乳腺癌等癌症的发病危险。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><b>【防晒】</b></span></u>：在炎热的夏天，番茄是比防晒霜更好的防晒工具。因为番茄富含抗氧化剂番茄红素，每天摄入<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>毫克番茄红素可将晒伤的危险系数下降<span lang=\"EN-US\">40%</span>。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、宜忌事项：</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一、不宜生吃。</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">尤其是</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">脾胃虚寒及月经期间的妇女。番茄含有大量可溶性收敛剂等成分，与胃酸发生反应，凝结成不溶解的块状物，容易引起胃肠胀满、疼痛等不适症状。如果只把番茄当成水果吃补充维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，或盛夏清暑热，则以生吃为佳。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二、不宜空腹吃。</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">空腹时</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">胃酸分泌量增多，因番茄所含的某种化学物质与胃酸结合易形成不溶于水的块状物，食之往往引起腹痛，造成胃不适、胃胀痛。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三、不宜吃未成熟的青色番茄。</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">因含有毒的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">龙葵碱。食用未成熟的青色番茄，会感到苦涩，多吃了，严重的可导致中毒，出现头晕、恶心、周身不适、呕吐及全身疲乏等症状，严重的还会发生生命危险。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四、不宜长时高温加热。</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">因番茄红素遇光、热和</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">氧气容易分解，失去保健作用。因此，烹调时应避免长时间高温加热。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">五、不宜和青瓜，黄瓜同食。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">青瓜含有一种维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>分解酶，会破坏其他蔬菜中的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，番茄富含维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，如果二者一起食用，达不到补充营养的效果。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">六、服用肝素、双香豆素等抗凝血药物时不宜食。</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">番茄含维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>较多，维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>主要催化肝中凝血酶原以及凝血活素的合成。维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>不足时，会使凝血时间延长造成皮下和肌肉出血。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">七、服用新斯的明或加兰他敏时禁食。</span></b></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">八、饭前吃番茄可瘦身。</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">番茄中的茄红素可以降低热量摄取，减少脂肪积累，并补充多种维生素，保持身体均衡营养。 番茄瘦身提倡饭前吃一个番茄，其中含有的食物纤维不为人体消化吸收，在减少米饭及高热量的菜肴摄食量的同时，阻止身体吸收食品中较多的脂肪。番茄独特的酸味还可刺激胃液分泌，促进肠胃蠕动，以帮助番茄中的食物纤维在肠内吸附多余的脂肪和废弃物一起排泄出来。对于寒性体质或胃肠虚弱的人则可选择加热过的番茄或番茄汁。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">孕妇吃番茄注意三件事</span></b></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一、要选择个大、圆润、丰满、外观漂亮的食用。不要吃长有赘生物的西红柿，因为这个赘生物是肿瘤。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二、不吃未成熟的西红柿：因为青色的西红柿含有大量的有毒番茄碱，孕妇食用后，会出现恶心、呕吐、全身乏力等中毒症状，对胎儿的发育有害。</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三、不要空腹吃：西红柿含有大量的胶质、果质、柿胶粉、可溶性收敛剂等成分。这些物质容易与胃酸起化学反应，结成不易溶解的块状物，阻塞胃出口引起腹痛。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red\">&nbsp; &ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red\">再安全的东西不好吃也不能持久！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>所以在好吃上，我下了功夫，主要从两方面，一品种、二有机肥。希望您尝尝看，缺点请多指正！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>西红柿寄语：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">自然生长的<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\">0</span>农药有机肥的西红柿，可以同时买个超市西红柿，首先切开看看内部的区别，再尝尝，区别不言而喻！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">7</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、保存方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">用几张白菜叶子把西红柿裹起来，困牢，扔放进冰箱里可以维持很久的新鲜。</span></span></p>', 'images/201211/thumb_img/103_thumb_G_1353871187122.jpg', 'images/201211/goods_img/103_G_1353871187565.jpg', 'images/201211/source_img/103_G_1353871187268.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1352241099', '100', '0', '1', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1361398779', '0', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('104', '9', 'ljf006', '“李家”绿翡翠生菜', '+strong', '105', '21', '', '10', '0.5', '9.60', '8.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '嫩绿的颜色、脆脆的口感，包烤肉、吃色拉，都是绝佳！', '<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、简介：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">（下图为实物图）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/ass3(1).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 生菜是叶用莴苣的俗称，属菊科莴苣属。为一年生或二年生草本作物，也是欧、美国家的大众蔬菜，深受人们喜爱。生菜原产欧洲地中海沿岸，由野生种驯化而来。古希腊人、罗马人最早食用。生菜传入我国的历史较悠久，东南沿海，特别是大城市近郊、两广地区栽培较多，特别是台湾种植尤为普遍。近年来，栽培面积迅速扩大，生菜也由宾馆、饭店进入寻常百姓的餐桌。</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、生菜的食疗作用：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我们在做</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">凉菜的时候，很多人都会想到生菜。从名字我们就不难看出，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><u>生菜是最合适生吃的蔬菜</u></strong></span>。生菜含有丰富的营养成分，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><strong>其纤维和维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>比白菜多</strong></u></span>，<u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong>有消除多余脂肪的作用</strong></span></u>。生菜除生吃、清炒外，还能与蒜蓉、蚝油、豆腐、菌菇同炒，不同的搭配，生菜所发挥的功效是不一样的。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　清炒生菜：具有生菜本身具备的功效，如镇痛催眠、降低胆固醇、辅助治疗神经衰弱、利尿、促进血液循环、抗病毒等。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">蒜蓉生菜：除了具有清炒生菜的功效外，还有杀菌、消炎和降血糖的作用，甚至还可以补脑。生菜含有丰富的维生素，具有防止牙龈出血以及维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>缺乏等功效。大蒜有解毒、行滞、健胃的功效，对脘腹冷痛、痢疾、泄泻、肺痨、百日咳、感冒、疟疾等症有一定的食疗作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">蚝油生菜：蚝油不是油质，而是在加工蚝豉（又名牡砺）时，煮蚝豉剩下的汤，此汤经过滤浓缩后即为蚝油。它是一种含多种营养成分、味道鲜美的调味作料。因此，蚝油生菜除有降血脂、降血压、降血糖、促进智力发育以及抗衰老等功效外，还能利尿、促进血液循环、抗病毒、预防与治疗心脏病及肝病。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　生菜与营养丰富的豆腐搭配食用，则是一种高蛋白、低脂肪、低胆固醇、多维生素的菜肴，具有清肝利胆，滋阴补肾，增白皮肤、减肥健美的作用。对目赤肿痛、肺热咳嗽、消渴、脾虚腹胀等也有一定的食疗作用<span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span>而菌菇含有丰富的易于人体吸收的蛋白质，并具有补脾益气、润燥化痰以及较强的滋补功效，与生菜搭配食用，对热咳、痰多、胸闷、吐泻等有一定的食疗作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从菜肴的食疗功效上讲，清炒生菜不如蚝油生菜和生菜炒菌菇的效果好。生菜炒豆腐营养价值虽然高，但对痛风病人来说，却要慎食，因豆腐含有较多的嘌呤物。而蚝油生菜、生菜炒菌菇比蒜蓉生菜更适合大众食用，食疗效果也更好。对于蒜蓉生菜，患有青光眼和白内障等眼病患者不宜经常食用。因为大蒜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>久食伤肝损眼<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、注意事项：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>烹饪注意事项</strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）对乙烯极为敏感，储藏时应远离苹果、梨和香蕉，以免诱发赤褐斑点</span></span></span></strong></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）无论是炒还是煮生菜，时间都不要太长，这样可以保持生菜脆嫩的口感</span></span></span></strong></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）生菜用手撕成片，吃起来会比刀切的脆</span></span></span></strong></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）将生菜洗净，加入适量沙拉酱直接食用，常食可有利于女性保持苗条的身材。</span></span></span></strong></u></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> </span><b style=\"line-height: 20.55pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">搭配宜忌</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">□</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">相宜的黄金搭配</span></span></span></strong></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&radic;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">生菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>兔肉<span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span>促进营养物质的消化和吸收</span></span></span></strong></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&radic;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">生菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>大蒜<span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span>清热解毒、提高人体免疫力</span></span></span></strong></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&radic;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">生菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>豆腐<span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span>排毒养颜</span></span></span></strong></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">□</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">相克的禁忌搭配</span></span></span></strong></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&times;</span>生菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>醋<span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span>降低营养价值</span></span></strong></u></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">5、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">6、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;绿翡翠</span>生菜寄语：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">嫩绿的颜色、脆脆的口感，包烤肉、吃色拉，都是绝佳！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">7、保存方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">储存时，将生菜的菜心摘除，然后将湿润的纸巾塞入菜心处让生菜吸收水分，等到纸巾较干时将其取出，再将生菜放入保鲜袋中冷藏。</span></span></p>', 'images/201303/thumb_img/104_thumb_G_1363405968843.jpg', 'images/201303/goods_img/104_G_1363405968436.jpg', 'images/201303/source_img/104_G_1363405968699.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1352241193', '100', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1363405968', '11', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('105', '9', 'ljf005', '“李家”小青菜', '+strong', '144', '21', '', '10', '0.5', '9.60', '8.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '青菜的原味——青丝味浓郁，尤其是到了夏季，当人们嫌弃青菜农药多没法吃时，你却可以大快朵颐，何等快事。', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、简介：</span></strong></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">（下图为实物图）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/xiaoqingcai.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">青菜是十字花科芸薹属的叶用蔬菜，学名<span lang=\"EN-US\">Brassica chinensis var chinensis</span>。在一些地方，青菜也可泛指绿色蔬菜。云南人也将苦菜称为青菜。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、青菜的食疗作用：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;1</span>）提供营养，强身健体 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><strong>青菜为含维生素和矿物质最丰富的蔬菜之一</strong></u></span>，一个成年人如果每天吃<span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span>克青菜，就能满足人体所需的维生素、胡萝卜素、钙、铁等，为保证身体的生理需要提供物质条件，有助于增强机体免疫能力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; 2</span>）<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><u>保持血管弹性 青菜中含有大量粗纤维</u></strong></span>，其进人人体内与脂肪结合后，可防止血浆胆固醇形成，促使胆固醇代谢物<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;&mdash;</span>胆酸得以排出体外，以减少动脉粥样硬化形成，从而保持血管弹性。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;3</span>）<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><u>润泽皮肤，延缓衰老</u></strong></span> 青菜中含有大量胡萝卜素（比豆类多<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>倍，比西红柿、瓜类多<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>倍）和维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，进入人体后，可促进皮肤细胞代谢；防止皮肤粗糙及色素沉着，使皮肤亮洁。延缓衰老。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;4</span>）<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><strong>防癌抗癌 青菜中所含的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，在体内会形成一种<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>透明质酸抑制物<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，这种物质具有抗癌作用，可使癌细胞丧失活力</strong></u></span>。此外，青菜中含有的粗纤维可促进大肠蠕动，增加大肠内毒素的排出，达到防癌抗癌的目的。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、青菜补钙比牛奶好：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span>牛奶是一种常喝的饮品，它提供给人体大量的钙，许多家庭每天必饮它而补钙。其实每天食用一些绿叶蔬菜就可以补充钙，其中青菜补钙量是最高的，比牛奶更好。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>牛奶有全脂与脱脂两种，可以形容它将钙稀释了，所以牛奶中的钙很容易被人体吸收。一杯奶就能轻松补足一日所需钙的三分之一，其他食品都不可能如此方便快捷。然而，事实上，如果按照营养素密度来计算，牛奶的补钙效益低于青菜。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>经过长时间计算，<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>克全脂牛奶能量约为<span lang=\"EN-US\">54</span>千卡，含钙<span lang=\"EN-US\">104</span>毫克。而<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>克小油菜含能量约为<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>千卡，含钙却高达<span lang=\"EN-US\">153</span>毫克。那么，按照钙营养素密度来计算，全脂牛奶为<span lang=\"EN-US\">104/54=1.9</span>，而小油菜是<span lang=\"EN-US\">153/15=10.2</span>，显然要高得多。同时，<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>克牛奶中的钾含量是<span lang=\"EN-US\">109</span>毫克，镁是<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>毫克。<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>克小油菜中的钾含量是<span lang=\"EN-US\">157</span>毫克，镁是<span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span>毫克，都比牛奶略高一些。镁本身就是骨骼的成分之一，而充足的钾和镁又有利于减少尿钙的流失。所以，一种食物能够同时供应大量钾、钙和镁，无疑是理想的健骨食品，何况绿叶菜中还含有丰富的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>，能帮助钙沉积入骨骼当中。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">所以如果按照相同食用量，绿叶菜的健骨矿物质比牛奶更多。小白菜、小油菜、羽衣甘蓝等甘蓝类蔬菜中含草酸较低，对钙的吸收利用妨碍较小。只要有充足的阳光照射，得到足够的维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">D</span>，其中的钙就可以充分实现营养价值。</span></strong></u><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>当然，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><u>这并不意味着奶类就失去了它的补钙意义</u></strong></span>。每日喝<span lang=\"EN-US\">250</span>克牛奶，只需要一分钟。吃<span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span>克绿叶蔬菜需要择菜、洗菜、炒菜或煮菜，要慢得多。所以，牛奶酸奶照喝，青菜多吃，不是得到的好处更多。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>小青菜寄语：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>青菜的原味<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;&mdash;</span>青丝味浓郁，尤其是到了夏季，当人们嫌弃青菜农药多没法吃时，你却可以大快朵颐，何等快事。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">7、保存方法：</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>若是青菜表面有水，则先把菜表面的水滴风干掉，然后放入袋子，一定记得放一张纸巾进去，在冰箱冷藏保存的时候，纸巾会吸附一些水气。这样，菜叶和菜梗儿就不会被湿漉漉的水分浸泡，也就不会腐烂，保存时间会就延长。若是青菜表面没水，则放入保鲜袋冷藏保存即可。</p>', 'images/201211/thumb_img/105_thumb_G_1353871166172.jpg', 'images/201211/goods_img/105_G_1353871166180.jpg', 'images/201211/source_img/105_G_1353871166882.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1352241236', '100', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1364938494', '11', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('106', '9', 'ljf004', '“李家”香菜', '+strong', '79', '21', '', '10', '0.3', '4.00', '4.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '一打开箱子，满鼻子的香菜味，味道比较正！', '<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、简介：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">（下图为实物图）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/xiangcai.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">香菜是人们最熟悉不过的提味蔬菜，北方一带人俗称<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>芫荽<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>状似芹，叶小且嫩，茎纤细，味郁香，是汤、饮中的佳佐。药用价值：起表出体外又可开胃消郁还可止痛解毒。</span><span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、香菜的食疗作用：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">　</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">中医认为，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">阴阳五行与人体有很大的关系，即人体有五脏六腑，五脏代表的就是五行。五脏是<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>心、肝、脾、胃、肾<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，五脏其神<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>喜、悲、怒、思、惊<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，五脏掌握着人体的生与死，香菜可调整人体五行，对人体有莫大的好处。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small; text-indent: 12pt;\">&nbsp; 香菜又名芫荽，为伞形科植物芫荽的带根全草，全国各地均有栽培，冬春采收，其植物的果实、种子亦供药用。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><strong>中医认为，香菜性味辛、温，入肺、脾经，有发汗透疹，消食下气之功，适用于感冒、小儿麻疹或风疹透发不畅、饮食积滞、消化不良等</strong></u></span>。《食经》言其<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>调食下气<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。《食疗本草》言其<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>利五脏，补筋脉，主消谷能食，治肠风<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。营养分析表明，香菜含挥发油、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、苹果酸钾等。香菜的香气是由醇类和烯类组成的挥发油及苹果酸钾引起的，入食后可增加胃液分泌，增进食欲，调节胃肠蠕动，提高消化力。山东中医药大学在对香菜的研究中发现，香菜不仅含有植物蛋白、钙、磷、铁、钾及多种维生素，而且还含有丰富的雌二醇、雌三醇，二者能调理女性性激素水平，促进排卵，为此，他们用香菜治疗排卵障碍所致的不孕症，取得了较好的效果，方法是水煎服，每日干品<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>克，鲜品为<span lang=\"EN-US\">150</span>克，也可将香菜捣汁，每日服用<span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span>毫升，也可将它作为药引子，放入中药里煎服。现介绍几则香菜食疗方。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　香菜粥 香菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>克，大米<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>克，调味品适量。将香菜洗净，切细<span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span>先取大米煮粥，煮至粥熟时下香菜及调味品等，再煮一二沸即成。每日<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>剂，连续<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>天。可解表散寒。适用于风寒感冒、麻疹疹出不畅等。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　香菜消食汤 香菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>克，神曲、陈皮各<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>克，生姜<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>片。将三者洗净，放入锅中，加清水适量水煎取汁，频频饮服，每日<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>剂，连续<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>天。可开胃健脾，适用于食欲不振、消化不良。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　香菜</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">香菇汤 香菜、香菇各<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>克。将二者洗净，放入锅中，加清水适量水煎取汁，频频饮服，每日<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>剂，连续<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>天。可解表透疹，适用于麻疹、风疹、水痘疹发不畅<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>疹已透或疹虽末透出而热毒壅盛者不宜服用<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">香菜葱姜汤 香菜、鲜葱、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">生姜各适量。将三者洗净，放入锅中，加清水适量水煎取汁，频频饮服，每日<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>剂，连续<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>天。可发汗解表，适用于风寒感冒、鼻塞流涕。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、民间传说：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; 据民间传说，</span><span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">商纣王昏庸，朝政荒芜，崇信妖妃，残害</span>忠良。周文王顺天意，主正义，集诸侯，讨伐商纣。赵公明逆天意，助商纣，命丧疆场。赵公明的三个妹子云霄、琼霄、碧霄为兄报仇，与姜子牙对阵。两军激战混乱中，杨戬放出了哮天犬，把碧霄的裤档一口扯烂了。碧霄害怕露出羞处，臊的两手捂住羞处蹲了下去。云霄、琼霄一下于赶了过来，捡起一块条石，照准哮天犬的后脑勺打去，一下子把哮天犬打的脑浆四喷。碧霄裤档被扯烂，失了贞体。恨死了哮天犬，把死犬拿来扒了皮，吃了狗肉。吃了肉，喝了汤，解了恨，嫌狗皮和狗爪扔在那搭恶心，就地挖了个小坑埋上。谁知哮天犬也是得道仙犬，它的毛长成一种香草，后人称为香菜。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">5、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">6、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;香菜</span>寄语：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">一打开箱子，满鼻子的香菜味，味道比较正！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">7、保存方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">香菜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要洗干净之后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">凉干</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">然后拿保鲜袋装好放入冰箱冷冻室里。等用的时候</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">拿出来一点用水冲一下即可，但要注意的是一定要凉干再放冰箱里。</span></span></p>', 'images/201211/thumb_img/106_thumb_G_1353871147969.jpg', 'images/201211/goods_img/106_G_1353871147701.jpg', 'images/201211/source_img/106_G_1353871147734.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1352241293', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1363732677', '0', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('107', '9', 'ljf003', '“李家”苦苣', '+strong', '104', '21', '', '10', '0.5', '9.60', '8.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '糖、醋、辣油、少许生抽，拌拌，大口吃，真是一个爽！', '<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#FF6600\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#FF6600\">、简介：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">（下图为实物图）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/kuju.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">苦苣<span lang=\"EN-US\">(endive)</span>菊科<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Compositae)</span>菊苣属中以嫩叶为食的栽培种，一二年生草本植物。学名<span lang=\"EN-US\">Cichorium endivia L.</span>，每<span lang=\"EN-US\">100g</span>嫩叶含水分<span lang=\"EN-US\">95.1g</span>、蛋白质<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.2g</span>、钙<span lang=\"EN-US\">77mg</span>及维生素等营养物质。<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><strong>适生食、煮食或作汤</strong></u></span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、苦苣的食疗作用：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">苦苣不仅在中国广为人知，在欧洲也有不少知音。据介绍，欧洲常见的苦苣菜其形状与中国苦苣十分相似，亦开 黄花，茎中空，折之有白色浆液流出。故欧洲民众俗称其为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;</span>牛奶菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;</span></strong></u></span>。欧洲农夫们普遍称苦苣菜为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><u><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>猪婆菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。据说母猪在产仔后只要经常喂给它新鲜苦苣菜就能增加其奶水，</u></strong></span>确保仔猪的健康成长。此外，苦苣菜在欧洲也是一种食用蔬菜，欧洲民众常采集嫩叶做色拉。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　苦苣菜又名苦菜，茎呈黄白色；叶片为圆状披针形，表面绿色，背面灰绿色；花鲜黄色。苦菜中含有丰富的钾、钙、镁、磷、钠、铁、等元素，能清热、消肿、化淤解毒、凉血止血。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">苦菜对</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">急性淋巴细胞性白血病、急性及慢性粒细胞白血病都有抑制作用</span></u></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。苦菜嫩叶可采食，生吃略带苦味，用开水烫一下制熟，苦味可除。苦菜可炒肉、做汤，或加些大豆粉做成小豆腐吃，亦可沸水烫后蘸面酱食用。或做麻酱拌苦菜、苦菜粥等。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">国际保健食品界的高度重视。研究表明：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><u>苦苣菜是一种出色的保健食品</u></strong></span>。苦苣菜的白浆中含<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>苦苣菜精<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>、树脂、大量维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>以及各种类黄酮成分。据说常食含苦苣菜的食品可防治多种细菌或病毒引起的感染症以及提高人体免疫能力。国外也开发出多种苦苣菜保健食品，其中包括含苦苣菜汁饮料、苦苣菜营养饼干、苦苣菜色拉酱等等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0px;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0px;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0px;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0px;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0px;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">4、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">5、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;苦苣</span>寄语：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">糖、醋、辣油、少许生抽，拌拌，大口吃，真是一个爽！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">6、保存方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将苦苣放入保鲜袋，再放到冰箱冷藏室保存。</span></span></p>', 'images/201302/thumb_img/107_thumb_G_1360878234836.jpg', 'images/201302/goods_img/107_G_1360878234720.jpg', 'images/201302/source_img/107_G_1360878234211.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1352241334', '100', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '1363020945', '0', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
