N-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 秧草</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">防出血：一切出血症候，如鼻血、龈血、吐血、咯血、便血、子宫出血、肛门出血。新药每用维他命<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>，认为是有凝结血管功能的疗法。其实维他命<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>在食品中，含量最丰富的，就是<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small;\">秧草</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 由</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small;\">秧草</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">来作为预防出血症候，实验的结果认为收效很高，对各种小出血，和肺胃及十二指肠出血，都能获得预防的效果。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 秧草</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的吃法，当然以新鲜为最佳，而且味亦隽美，因为新鲜的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small;\">秧草</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，四季皆有，即使在寒冷季节，亦有出产，不过由於气候和土地的关系，有时产品极嫩，有时极老，患者不妨常用此佐膳，可以防止出血。用盐渍制的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>腌</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small;\">秧草</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，功效相等。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small;\">秧草</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">的嫩叶，是我们理想的蔬菜，因为极富营养，在绿叶蔬菜中，它的维他命<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>的含量最高，特别是维他命<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>含量和胡萝卜相差极微，维他命<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>超过白萝卜二三倍以上，这些营养成分都超过菠菜。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">3、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/shanghuilijianfeng.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red\">&nbsp; &ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red\">再安全的东西不好吃也不能持久！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>所以在好吃上，我下了功夫，主要从两方面，一品种、二有机肥。希望您尝尝看，缺点请多指正！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">4、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;秧草</span>寄语：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">无论是清炒秧草，还是河蚌秧草，这秧草都满鲜！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">5、保存方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将秧草放入保鲜袋，再放到冰箱冷藏室保存。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201211/thumb_img/108_thumb_G_1353871111521.jpg', 'images/201211/goods_img/108_G_1353871111535.jpg', 'images/201211/source_img/108_G_1353871111772.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1352241456', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1361398753', '0', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('109', '9', 'ljf001', '“李家”包菜', '+strong', '183', '21', '', '1', '1.0', '19.20', '16.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '嫩、脆、甜，建议别切丝，手撕撕即可，因为这样可以保留充足的纤维素，做手撕包菜还是很合适的！', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#FF6600\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#FF6600\">、简介：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">结球甘蓝（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Brassica oleracea L.var.capitata L.</span>）是十字花科、芸薹属的植物，为甘蓝（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Brassica oleracea L.</span>）的变种。又名卷心菜、洋白菜、疙瘩白、包菜、圆白菜、包心菜、莲花白等。起源于地中海沿岸，<span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span>世纪开始传入中国。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、包菜的食疗作用：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">包菜即圆白菜，它的营养丰富，味道鲜美，在我们在饭店吃的炒饼用的菜就是它，如果用其他蔬菜，炒饼的味道会变味。包菜还有很好的食疗保健作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<b>富含叶酸</b></span></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜含有丰富的叶酸，叶酸属于维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>的复合体，它对巨幼细胞贫血和胎儿畸形有很好的预防作用，所以怀孕的女人及生长发育期的儿童应该多吃点圆白菜。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　富含丰富维生素</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜和大白菜一样富含维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>和胡萝卜素等，圆白菜的总维生素含量比番茄高三倍，所以它具有很好的抗氧化作用及抗衰老作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<b>　杀菌、消炎</b></span></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜如果新鲜的话，还会有消炎、杀菌的作用。咽喉疼痛、外伤肿痛、胃痛、牙痛时，可以将圆白菜榨汁后饮下或涂于患处。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　杀死白细胞</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">患有白血病的人可以多食用圆白菜，圆白菜含有丰富的异硫氰酸丙酯衍生体，这种物质可以杀死体内导致白血病的异常细胞。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　治疗溃疡</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜富含维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">U</span>，维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">U</span>对溃疡有很好的治疗作用，能加速溃疡的愈合，还能预防胃溃疡恶变。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　抗癌作用</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜中含有丰富的吲哚类化合物。实验证明，<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>吲哚<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>具有抗癌作用，可以避免人类罹患肠癌。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　刺激生成有益酶</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜中含有丰富的萝卜硫素。这种物质能刺激人体细胞产生对身体有益的酶，进而形成一层对抗外来致癌物侵蚀的保护膜。萝卜硫素是迄今为止所发现的蔬菜中最强的抗癌成分。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　减肥作用</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卷心菜含有的热量和脂肪很低，但是维生素、膳食纤维和微量元素的含量却很高，是一种很棒的减肥食物。翻炒后的卷心菜和辣椒一起搭配，能促进我们肠胃的蠕动，快速排出身体咯多余的垃圾，起到瘦身减肥的效果。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small; text-indent: 24pt;\">&nbsp; 由此可见，人们为了自身的健康应该常吃圆白菜。营养学家指出，圆白菜生吃的食疗保健效果最好。我们可以将圆白菜凉拌、做沙拉或榨汁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: small; text-indent: 24pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:24.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、适合人群：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">）特别适合动脉硬化、胆结石症患者、肥胖患者、孕妇及有消化道溃疡食用。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">2</span><span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">）但皮肤瘙痒性疾病、眼部充血患者忌食。包心菜含有粗纤维量多，且质硬，故脾胃虚寒、泄泻以及小儿脾弱者不宜多食；另外对于腹腔和胸外科手术后，胃肠溃疡及其出血特别严重时，腹泻及肝病时不宜吃。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/shanghuilijianfeng.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red\">&nbsp; &ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red\">再安全的东西不好吃也不能持久！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>所以在好吃上，我下了功夫，主要从两方面，一品种、二有机肥。希望您尝尝看，缺点请多指正！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#FF6600\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#FF6600\">、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;包菜</span>寄语：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">嫩、脆、甜，建议别切丝，手撕撕即可，因为这样可以保留充足的纤维素，做手撕包菜还是很合适的！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、保存方法：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将紫包菜放入保鲜袋，再放到冰箱冷藏室保存，尽早食用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201211/thumb_img/109_thumb_G_1353871082766.jpg', 'images/201211/goods_img/109_G_1353871082412.jpg', 'images/201211/source_img/109_G_1353871082403.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1352241607', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1363405217', '0', '', '0', '0', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('112', '11', 'ljf032', '“李家”药芹', '+strong', '133', '21', '', '10', '0.5', '9.60', '8.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '清香、劲脆的蔬菜，别忘了芹菜叶其实是最有营养的一个部分哦~', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、简介：</span></strong></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: small; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">（下图为实物图）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/qin1.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 芹菜，属伞形科植物。有水芹、旱芹两种，功能相近，药用以旱芹为佳。旱芹香气较浓，又名<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>香芹<span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;</span>，亦称<span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;</span>药芹<span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;</span>。芹菜是<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><u>高纤维食物</u></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>它经肠内消化作用产生一种木质素或肠内脂的物质，这类物质是一种抗氧化剂，<strong><u><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">常吃芹菜，尤其是吃芹菜叶，对预防高血压、动脉硬化等都十分有益</span></u></strong>，并有辅助治疗作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、芹菜的食疗作用：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）芹菜镇静安神。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 从芹菜子中分离出的一种碱性成分，对动物有镇静作用，对人体能起安定作用；芹菜甘或芹菜素口服能对抗可卡因引起的小鼠兴奋，有利于安定情绪，消除烦躁。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）芹菜利尿消肿。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜含有利尿有效成分，消除体内水钠潴留，利尿消肿。临床上以芹菜水煎有效率达<span lang=\"EN-US\">85. 7%</span>，可治疗乳糜尿。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>）芹菜平肝降压。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜含酸性的降压成分，对兔、犬静脉注射有明显降压作用；血管灌流可使血管扩张；用主动脉弓灌流法，它能对抗烟碱、山梗茶碱引起的升压反应，并可引起降压。临床对于原发性、妊娠性及更年期高血压均有效。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）芹菜养血补虚。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜含铁量较高，能补充妇女经血的损失，食之能避免皮肤苍白、干燥、面色无华，而且可使目光有神，头发黑亮。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>）芹菜清热解毒。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　春季气候干燥，人们往往感到口干舌燥气喘心烦，身体不适，常吃些芹菜有助于清热解毒，去病强身。肝火过旺，皮肤粗糙及经常失眠、头疼的人可适当多吃些。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>）芹菜也是一种理想的绿色减肥食品。因为当你嘴巴里正在咀嚼芹菜的同时，你消耗的热能远大于芹菜给予你的能量。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>）芹菜<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><u>防癌抗癌</u></strong></span>。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜是高纤维食物，它经肠内消化作用产生一种木质素或肠内脂的物质，这类物质是一种抗氧化剂，高浓度时可抑制肠内细菌产生的致癌物质。它还可以加快粪便在肠内的运转时间；减少致癌物与结肠粘膜的接触达到预防结肠癌的目的。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>）芹菜<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><u>醒酒保胃</u></strong></span>。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜属于高纤维食物，可以加快胃部的消化和排除，然后通过芹菜的利尿功能，把胃部的酒精通过尿液排出体外，以此缓解胃部的压力，起到醒酒保胃的效果。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>）从芹菜子中分离出的一种碱性成分，对动物有镇静作用，对人体能起安定作用；芹菜甘或芹菜素口服能对抗可卡因引起的小鼠兴奋，有利于安定情绪，消除烦躁。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜降血压、镇静、镇痉；健胃、利尿、净血、调经；清热除烦，平肝，利水消肿，凉血止血；主治高血压，头痛，头晕，暴热烦渴，黄疸，水肿，小便热涩不利，妇女月经不调，赤白带下，瘰疬，痄腮等病症。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　高血压，头痛脑胀，颜面潮红，精神易兴奋者：鲜芹菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">250</span>克，洗净，以沸开水烫约<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>分钟，切细捣绞汁， 每次服<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>小杯，一<span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>次。可使血压下降，自觉症状随之消除。 如无鲜莱可用干菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>－<span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span>克，水煎服<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>鲜菜用沸开水烫后晾干，便为干菜，可保存备用<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　妇女月经不调，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">崩中带下，或小便出血：鲜芹菜<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>克，茜草<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>克，六月雪<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>克，水煎服。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜所含芹菜素有降压作用，其作用主要是通过颈动脉体化学感受器的反射作用而引起。芹菜的生物碱提取物对动物有镇静作用。用于肝经有热，肝阳上亢，烦热不安，眩晕；热淋，尿浊，小便不利或尿血；月经先期；胃热呕逆，饮食减少。现代用于高血压病、乳糜尿等。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 芹菜生吃可降压：芹菜具有消炎、降压、镇静、消热止咳、健胃利尿等作用，经常食用能除烦热、下淤血。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 芹菜的降压作用炒熟后并不明显，最好生吃或凉拌，连叶带茎一起嚼食，可以最大程度地保存营养，起到降压的作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、芹菜叶更有营养：</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 吃芹菜的时候通常把芹菜叶给弄掉，其实这样是不正确的。叶比茎的营养要高出很多倍，芹菜中含有蛋白质、脂肪、碳水化合物、粗纤维、钙、磷、铁等多种营养物质，同时具有较高的药用价值。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　其性凉、味甘、无毒，具有散热、祛风利湿、健胃利血、清肠利便、润肺止咳、降低血压、健脑镇静的作用，对高血压、血管硬化、神经衰弱等有辅助治疗作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　叶比茎的营养要高出很多倍</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　人们通常在吃芹菜时，先要摘去叶子，然后用芹菜的茎入菜。营养专家指出，叶比茎的营养要高出很多倍，所以扔掉芹菜叶实在可惜。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　很多人吃芹菜时只吃茎而扔掉叶子，其实，从营养学上来说，芹菜叶比茎的营养要高出很多倍，还有抑制癌症的作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜的营养十分丰富，含有蛋白质、脂肪、碳水化合物、粗纤维、钙、磷、铁等多种营养物质。其中，蛋白质含量比一般的瓜果蔬菜高<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>倍，铁的含量是番茄的<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>倍左右，还含丰富的胡萝卜素和多种维生素。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　此外，芹菜中含有一种挥发性芳香油，会散发出特殊的香味，可以促进食欲。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜具有较高的药用价值</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜具有较高的药用价值。其性凉，味甘，无毒，具有散热、祛风利湿、健胃利血、清肠利便、润肺止咳、降低血压、健脑镇静的作用，对高血压、血管硬化、神经衰弱、头痛脑涨、小儿软骨症等都有辅助治疗作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　近年来的研究还表明，多吃芹菜还可以增强人体的抗病能力。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　国外科学家发现，由于芹菜中富含水分和纤维，并含有一种能使脂肪加速分解、消失的化学物质，因此是减肥的最佳食品。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　营养学家曾对芹菜的茎和叶片进行过<span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span>项营养成分的测试，发现芹菜叶的营养成分中，有<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>项指标超过了茎。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　芹菜叶中胡萝卜素含量是茎的<span lang=\"EN-US\">88</span>倍</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　其中，芹菜叶中胡萝卜素含量是茎的<span lang=\"EN-US\">88</span>倍、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>含量是茎的<span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span>倍、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B1</span>含量是茎的<span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span>倍、蛋白质含量是茎的<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>倍、钙的含量则超过茎<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>倍。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 此外，经有关研究实验发现，芹菜叶对癌症还具有一定的抑制作用，抑制率可以达到<span lang=\"EN-US\">73%</span>。把它榨汁后做成饮料，据说有很好的兴奋作用。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; 所以，芹菜叶入菜营养胜过芹菜茎，那种<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><u>只吃芹菜茎不吃芹菜叶的习惯应该改掉</u></strong></span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">5、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">6、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>药芹寄语：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 脆、很清香！<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">7、保存方法：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; 用保鲜袋或者保鲜膜茎叶部分包严，然后芹菜根部朝下竖起放入清水盆洗净后切成大段，整齐地放入饭盒或者干净的保鲜封好。</span></p>', 'images/201302/thumb_img/112_thumb_G_1361674716874.jpg', 'images/201302/goods_img/112_G_1361674716739.jpg', 'images/201302/source_img/112_G_1361674716381.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1354557516', '100', '0', '1', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1363732674', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
