</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>1）黑心乌秋季播种，以经霜雪后味甜美而著称，被视为白菜中的珍品，因其中含有大量的膳食纤维、钙、铁、维生素C、维生素B1、维生素B2、胡萝卜素等,也被称为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><u><strong>&ldquo;维生素&rdquo;菜</strong></u></span> 。</p>\r\n<p>2）<span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px;\">黑心乌</span>中的膳食纤维，对<u><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">防治便秘有</span></strong></u>很好的作用。</p>\r\n<p>3）祖国医学早在《食物本草》中记载：&ldquo;塌菜甘、平、无毒。能滑肠、疏肝、利五脏。&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>4）常吃<span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px;\">黑心乌</span>还可以增强人体抗病能力，泽肤健美。</p>\r\n<p>5）<span style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px;\">黑心乌</span>口感清新爽脆，最适合炒食，清炒或加入肉丝、火腿丝一起炒均可。</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3、上会佰亩杉农场简介：&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c2.jpg\" width=\"646\" height=\"604\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c5.jpg\" width=\"772\" height=\"514\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">4、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: red;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"fo