: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 30px;\">菜心主要吃的是嫩叶和嫩薹，可炒菜、可做汤，味道鲜美，清爽可口！</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-family: 宋体;\">7、保存方法：</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none;\">&nbsp;</span>若是菜心表面有水，则先把菜表面的水滴风干掉，然后放入袋子，一定记得放一张纸巾进去，在冰箱冷藏保存的时候，纸巾会吸附一些水气。这样，菜叶和菜梗儿就不会被湿漉漉的水分浸泡，也就不会腐烂，保存时间会就延长。若是青菜表面没水，则放入保鲜袋冷藏保存即可。</span></p>', 'images/201302/thumb_img/128_thumb_G_1361662205177.jpg', 'images/201302/goods_img/128_G_1361662205367.jpg', 'images/201302/source_img/128_G_1361662205198.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1361661144', '100', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '1362269110', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
