4\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">5、蔬菜生产农户李建峰（右）给大家的一句话：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/images/upload/Image/li.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/piyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">6、原味生活<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>李家<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>生菜寄语：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><font size=\"2\">我想不用多说了，这是一款很好吃、受欢迎的生菜品种！</font></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">7、保存方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">储存时，将生菜的菜心摘除，然后将湿润的纸巾塞入菜心处让生菜吸收水分，等到纸巾较干时将其取出，再将生菜放入保鲜袋中冷藏。</span></span></p>', 'images/201303/thumb_img/142_thumb_G_1363128667441.jpg', 'images/201303/goods_img/142_G_1363128667299.jpg', 'images/201303/source_img/142_G_1363128667606.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1363128667', '100', '0', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '1363153850', '11', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '', '0农药有机肥');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check`, `biaozhun` ) VALUES  ('143', '9', 'ljf060', '“李家”伏玉包菜', '+strong', '15', '21', '', '10', '0.5', '8.00', '8.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '1', '', '嫩、脆、甜，建议别切丝，手撕撕即可，因为这样可以保留充足的纤维素，做手撕包菜很合适！', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">1</span></strong><strong style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、简介：</span></strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Verdana, Arial; font-size: small; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">（下图为实物图）</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/add1.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;</span>结球甘蓝（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Brassica oleracea L.var.capitata L.</span>）是十字花科、芸薹属的植物，为甘蓝（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Brassica oleracea L.</span>）的变种。又名卷心菜、洋白菜、疙瘩白、包菜、圆白菜、包心菜、莲花白等。起源于地中海沿岸，<span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span>世纪开始传入中国。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、包菜的食疗作用：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">包菜即圆白菜，它的营养丰富，味道鲜美，在我们在饭店吃的炒饼用的菜就是它，如果用其他蔬菜，炒饼的味道会变味。包菜还有很好的食疗保健作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　<b>富含叶酸</b></span></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜含有丰富的叶酸，叶酸属于维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>的复合体，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong>它对巨幼细胞贫血和胎儿畸形有很好的预防作用，所以怀孕的女人及生长发育期的儿童应该多吃点圆白菜</strong></span>。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　富含丰富维生素</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜和大白菜一样富含维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>和胡萝卜素等，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong>圆白菜的总维生素含量比番茄高三倍，所以它具有很好的抗氧化作用及抗衰老作用</strong></span>。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　<b>　杀菌、消炎</b></span></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜如果新鲜的话，还会<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong>有消炎、杀菌的作用</strong></span>。咽喉疼痛、外伤肿痛、胃痛、牙痛时，可以将圆白菜榨汁后饮下或涂于患处。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　杀死白细胞</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">患有白血病的人可以多食用圆白菜</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，圆白菜含有丰富的异硫氰酸丙酯衍生体，这种物质可以杀死体内导致白血病的异常细胞。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　治疗溃疡</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜富含维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">U</span>，<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">U</span>对溃疡有很好的治疗作用</span></strong>，能加速溃疡的愈合，还能预防胃溃疡恶变。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　抗癌作用</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜中含有丰富的吲哚类化合物。实验证明，<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>吲哚<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>具有抗癌作用，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong>可以避免人类罹患肠癌</strong></span>。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　刺激生成有益酶</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">圆白菜中含有丰富的萝卜硫素。这种物质能刺激人体细胞产生对身体有益的酶，进而形成一层对抗外来致癌物侵蚀的保护膜。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">萝卜硫素是迄今为止所发现的蔬菜中最强的抗癌成分。</span></strong></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">　　减肥作用</span></b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卷心菜含有的热量和脂肪很低，但是维生素、膳食纤维和微量元素的含量却很高，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong>是一种很棒的减肥食物</strong></span>。翻炒后的卷心菜和辣椒一起搭配，能促进我们肠胃的蠕动，快速排出身体咯多余的垃圾，起到瘦身减肥的效果。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 24pt;\">&nbsp; 由此可见，人们为了自身的健康应该常吃圆白菜。营养学家指出，圆白菜生吃的食疗保健效果最好。我们可以将圆白菜凉拌、做沙拉或榨汁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">、适合人群：</span></strong></span><span lang=\"